#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:13
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "被感染的无人机舰体碎裂，你唯一的选择就是打捞剩下的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:25
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_CONTACTGAMBLE_SUCCESS\"]/text"
msgstr "无人机停下来，向你倾斜过来。然而，当它靠近时，一些包裹在它上面的灵魂瘟疫粘质"
"会松弛下来，融入到你的船体中..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:30
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_CONTACTGAMBLE_SUCCESS\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:32
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_CONTACTGAMBLE_SUCCESS\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……它一路侵入内部，汇聚成了一大群躯壳！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:39
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_CONTACTGAMBLE_FAILURE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"无人机骤然停下，但它的系统受损程度比你想象的还要严重。它将你试图接触的行为判"
"定为挑衅，随即上前发起攻击！当它逼近时，附着在它身上的部分灵魂瘟疫黏液脱落下"
"来，渗入你飞船的船壳，进入内部后最终汇聚成一大群灵魂瘟疫躯壳……看来你遇上了双"
"重麻烦！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:43
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_CONTACTGAMBLE_FAILURE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:55
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_SALVAGEGAMBLE_SUCCESS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你成功靠近了这架无人机，将其拆解回收零件，但难以处理带回的受灵魂瘟疫感染物质"
"。附着在部分战利品上的虹色黏液松脱，掉落在地面……随后凝聚成一大群空壳怪！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:61
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_SALVAGEGAMBLE_FAILURE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"尽管你成功靠近了无人机，但其系统受损程度却远没有你想象的严重。它将你试图回收"
"它的行为判定为挑衅，并准备进行自卫！与此同时，附着在机身上的部分灵魂瘟疫黏液"
"脱落，渗入你的飞船船体，最终在内部凝聚成一大群灵魂瘟疫空壳怪……看来你陷入了双"
"重危机！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:65
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_SALVAGEGAMBLE_FAILURE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:71
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_FIXED\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"空壳怪已经解决，你的注意力重新回到外面的无人机上。它似乎一直在附近耐心等候，"
"这时你收到一段来自它的自动语音录音：联联联……邦！欢欢欢迎！你不清楚它为何会出"
"现在此地，也不明白它为何还能勉强运转，但它似乎仍有货物可供交易。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:83
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:89
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_REAL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"能在这么远的地方看到一张熟悉的面孔，本该是种慰藉……可在这座信标等候你的联邦舰"
"船，只是一艘自动舰船。更糟的是，它似乎因灵魂瘟疫物质病毒的侵袭，内部结构与外"
"部船体都遭受了严重损毁。这艘自动舰船的外壳微微泛光，行动也断断续续，但你感觉"
"，只要能想办法让它减速，或许依然可以和它进行交易。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:92
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_REAL\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "尝试联系无人机。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:96
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_REAL\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "回收该无人机。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:100
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_REAL\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_ALIGNED\"]/text"
msgstr "(灵魂瘟疫船员) 修理这架无人机……？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:102
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_REAL\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_ALIGNED\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你麾下受灵魂瘟疫侵染的船员发出一阵咕噜声，一丝微弱的低语拂过你的脑海。外面的"
"自动舰船缓缓停下，你收到一段来自它的自动语音录音：联联联……邦！欢欢欢迎！你不"
"清楚它为何会出现在此地，也不明白它为何还能勉强运转，但它似乎仍有货物可供交易"
"。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:107
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_REAL\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_ENGI\"]/text"
msgstr "(半械族船员)修理该无人机。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:109
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_REAL\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_ENGI\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的半械族对修理自动舰船和无人机早已熟稔，尽管它从未见过被物质病毒侵染的个体"
"。它将无人机修复到能够静止的程度，但附着在无人机上的部分灵魂瘟疫黏液脱落，融"
"进了你的飞船船体……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:114
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_REAL\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_ENGI\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:116
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_REAL\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_ENGI\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……在潜入内部之后，汇聚成了一群空壳怪！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:123
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_REAL\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_ENGINEER\"]/text"
msgstr "(工程师船员)修理无人机。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:125
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_REAL\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_ENGINEER\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的工程师试图解释，他们只习惯修理叛军自动舰船，从未修理过被灵魂瘟疫感染的船"
"只，但你还是说服他们尝试一下。他们将无人机修复到能够静止的程度，但附着在上面"
"的部分灵魂瘟疫黏液脱落，融进了你的飞船船体……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:130
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_REAL\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_ENGINEER\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:132
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_REAL\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_ENGINEER\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……随后渗入船内，汇聚成一群空壳怪！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:139
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_REAL\"]/choice[@req=\"DRONE_CONTROL_REPAIR_ALL\"]/text"
msgstr "(维修无人机)修复该无人机。[1|]"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:141
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_REAL\"]/choice[@req=\"DRONE_CONTROL_REPAIR_ALL\"]/event/text"
msgstr "你的维修无人机开始修复这艘自动舰船。它将舰船修复到能够静止的程度，但附着在舰"
"船上的部分灵魂瘟疫黏液脱落，融进了你的飞船船体……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:149
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_REAL\"]/choice[@req=\"DRONE_CONTROL_REPAIR_ALL\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:151
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_REAL\"]/choice[@req=\"DRONE_CONTROL_REPAIR_ALL\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……随后渗入船内，汇聚成一群空壳怪！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:158
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_REAL\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_LANIUS\"]/text"
msgstr "(食铁族船员)让你的食铁族船员回收无人机。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:160
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_REAL\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_LANIUS\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的食铁族能够拆解回收这架无人机，它清楚该拆卸哪些部件以避免触发防御系统，但"
"它并未做好应对随之一同带回的灵魂瘟疫感染物质的准备。附着在部分舰体上的虹色黏"
"液脱落，掉落在地板上……随后汇聚成了一群空壳怪！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:166
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_REAL\"]/choice[8]/text"
msgstr "无视这艘自动舰船。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:168
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_REAL\"]/choice[8]/event/text"
msgstr "这台故障的自动机械歪歪扭扭地驶离，深入星云之中，你不禁好奇，在它的系统彻底失"
"效之前，还会漫无目的地漂泊多久。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:170
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_REAL\"]/choice[8]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:174
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_CORRUPTEDDRONE_REAL\"]/choice[8]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:183
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_FEDERATIONREMAINS_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "这艘联邦舰船仅存的残骸四散纷飞，消失在星云的云雾之中。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:195
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_FEDERATIONREMAINS_INVESTIGATION_FAILURE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你下令调查这艘残破舰船的内部。令你惊讶的是，它的系统不知为何仍在供电；微弱、"
"沉闷的气流吹拂着舰船昏暗的走廊。但你很快就弄清了先前船员的遭遇——墙壁、地板和"
"天花板上都覆盖着厚厚的灵魂瘟疫物质病毒，这里的病毒甚至比舰船本身还要多。你不"
"顾一切地下令撤退，可已经太迟了；你周围的物质开始冒泡，空壳怪正从四周的墙壁中"
"挣脱出来。万幸的是，你成功逃回了自己的飞船，可空壳怪也紧随其后追了上来！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:207
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_FEDERATIONREMAINS_INVESTIGATION_MINORSUCCESS_ACTIVATION_BATTLE_LOOT\"]/text"
msgstr "最后一只空壳怪融化成一滩液体落在地板上，你将注意力转回悬停在外的自动舰船。你"
"知道它仅剩的能量仅能完成一个请求。你会选择什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:209
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_FEDERATIONREMAINS_INVESTIGATION_MINORSUCCESS_ACTIVATION_BATTLE_LOOT\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "发送修复指令。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:211
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_FEDERATIONREMAINS_INVESTIGATION_MINORSUCCESS_ACTIVATION_BATTLE_LOOT\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你向无人机的系统发送指令，它随即开始修复你的舰体。它修复了几分钟，随后灯光开"
"始闪烁，接着彻底熄灭，自动舰船静止不动……它的任务完成了。你希望它能在这里，代"
"替你陨落的联邦盟友安心安息。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:216
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_FEDERATIONREMAINS_INVESTIGATION_MINORSUCCESS_ACTIVATION_BATTLE_LOOT\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "发送获取资源的指令。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:218
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_FEDERATIONREMAINS_INVESTIGATION_MINORSUCCESS_ACTIVATION_BATTLE_LOOT\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你向无人机的系统发送指令，它准备抛射出所载货物。完成这一切后，它的灯光开始闪"
"烁，随后彻底熄灭，自动舰船静止不动……它的任务完成了。你希望它能在这里，代替你"
"陨落的联邦盟友安心安息。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:223
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_FEDERATIONREMAINS_INVESTIGATION_MINORSUCCESS_ACTIVATION_BATTLE_LOOT\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "下达指令，让它牵制叛军舰队。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:225
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_FEDERATIONREMAINS_INVESTIGATION_MINORSUCCESS_ACTIVATION_BATTLE_LOOT\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你向无人机的系统发送指令，它准备用尽剩余能量，全力发出一道联邦信号。完成这一"
"切后，它的灯光开始闪烁，随后彻底熄灭，自动舰船静止不动……它的任务完成了。你希"
"望它能在这里，代替你陨落的联邦盟友安心安息。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:232
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_FEDERATIONREMAINS_INVESTIGATION_MINORSUCCESS_ACTIVATION_BATTLE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你按下自动舰船上的按钮，它瞬间轰鸣启动……它即将在片刻后展开部署，你意识到必须"
"在它升空并撕裂舰体之前离开这里！你飞奔穿过破损舰船里霉味弥漫的走廊，随着无人"
"机准备起飞，你周围那些虹色的水洼也随之震动，而你及时赶了回来……就在你返回的同"
"时，自动舰船猛地从联邦舰船的残骸中挣脱出来。它的舰体碎裂，残骸四散飞溅，自动"
"舰船悬停在外侧……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:238
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_FEDERATIONREMAINS_INVESTIGATION_MINORSUCCESS_ACTIVATION_BATTLE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:240
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_FEDERATIONREMAINS_INVESTIGATION_MINORSUCCESS_ACTIVATION_BATTLE\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……但似乎有一大群空壳怪被惊醒，在那之前就跟着你登上了飞船！你必须先解决掉它们…"
"…"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:247
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_FEDERATIONREMAINS_INVESTIGATION_MINORSUCCESS_ACTIVATION_LUCKY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你按下自动舰船上的按钮，它瞬间轰鸣启动……它即将在片刻后展开部署，你意识到必须"
"在它升空并撕裂舰体之前离开这里！你飞奔穿过破损舰船里霉味弥漫的走廊，随着无人"
"机准备起飞，你周围那些虹色水洼也随之震动，而你及时赶了回来。你关上身后的气密"
"舱，你的飞船随即分离，此时灵魂瘟疫空壳怪正源源不断地涌出来；它们朝飞船扑来，"
"却差了一点……它们似乎只能永远在这片星云中宣泄它们贪婪的能量。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:249
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_FEDERATIONREMAINS_INVESTIGATION_MINORSUCCESS_ACTIVATION_LUCKY\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "等待无人机发射。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:251
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_FEDERATIONREMAINS_INVESTIGATION_MINORSUCCESS_ACTIVATION_LUCKY\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"片刻之后，自动舰船猛地从联邦舰船的残骸中挣脱出来。它的舰体碎裂，残骸四散飞溅"
"，自动舰船悬停在外侧……你知道它仅剩的能量仅能完成一个请求。你会选择什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:254
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_FEDERATIONREMAINS_INVESTIGATION_MINORSUCCESS_ACTIVATION_LUCKY\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "发送修复指令。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:256
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_FEDERATIONREMAINS_INVESTIGATION_MINORSUCCESS_ACTIVATION_LUCKY\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你向无人机的系统发送指令，它随即开始修复你的舰体。它修复了几分钟，随后灯光开"
"始闪烁，接着彻底熄灭，自动舰船静止不动……它的任务完成了。你希望它能在这里，代"
"替你陨落的联邦盟友安心安息。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:261
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_FEDERATIONREMAINS_INVESTIGATION_MINORSUCCESS_ACTIVATION_LUCKY\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "发送获取资源的指令。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:263
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_FEDERATIONREMAINS_INVESTIGATION_MINORSUCCESS_ACTIVATION_LUCKY\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你向无人机的系统发送指令，它准备抛射出所载货物。完成这一切后，它的灯光开始闪"
"烁，随后彻底熄灭，自动舰船静止不动……它的任务完成了。你希望它能在这里，代替你"
"陨落的联邦盟友安心安息。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:268
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_FEDERATIONREMAINS_INVESTIGATION_MINORSUCCESS_ACTIVATION_LUCKY\"]/choice/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "下达指令，让它牵制叛军舰队。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:270
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_FEDERATIONREMAINS_INVESTIGATION_MINORSUCCESS_ACTIVATION_LUCKY\"]/choice/event/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你向无人机的系统发送指令，它准备用尽剩余能量，全力发出一道联邦信号。完成这一"
"切后，它的灯光开始闪烁，随后彻底熄灭，自动舰船静止不动……它的任务完成了。你希"
"望它能在这里，代替你陨落的联邦盟友安心安息。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:279
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_FEDERATIONREMAINS_INVESTIGATION_MINORSUCCESS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你决定调查这艘残破飞船的内部。令你意外的是，它的系统不知为何仍在供电，微弱浑"
"浊的气流在昏暗的船舱里流动。地板上散落着几滩灵魂瘟疫物质病毒，你大致能猜到船"
"上的人遭遇了什么。你小心翼翼地绕过病毒，继续深入，意外发现了飞船的货舱。残骸"
"里停着一艘未启用的自动舰船，你认出它正是储存信标的来源。可惜的是，在船员遇难"
"前，它从未被妥善装载补给……即便启动，它的能量也只够完成一项任务。更糟的是，你"
"余光瞥见黑暗中另一滩病毒正在微微发光……值得冒险惊动它吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:281
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_FEDERATIONREMAINS_INVESTIGATION_MINORSUCCESS\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "启动无人机。"

