#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:668
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUGPARANOIA_REAL_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
