#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:675
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUGPARANOIA_REAL_FIGHT_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr "蛞蝓族的舰船已经被摧毁，不用说这里也不会有任何交易了……算了。是时候继续前进了"
"。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:686
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUGPARANOIA\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:692
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUGPARANOIA_REAL\"]/text"
msgstr "你在进入信标时猛地一惊，立刻收到了数十个请求通讯的提示音，视线望向星云外的那"
"艘蛞蝓族舰船。至少你能确定它们不是空壳怪，但这种行为依旧十分诡异。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:695
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUGPARANOIA_REAL\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "接听其中一个通讯请求。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:697
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUGPARANOIA_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你向蛞蝓族发起通讯，视频接通的瞬间你又被吓了一跳。一只蛞蝓族把脸紧紧贴在镜头"
"上，它急切地说道：“你不是那些僵尸怪物吧？对不对？证明给我看！转过去！”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:699
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUGPARANOIA_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_ALIGNED\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "顺着蛞蝓族的意，转过身去。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:701
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUGPARANOIA_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_ALIGNED\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你转过身，屏幕里的蛞蝓族声音稍稍平复了下来：“好了，好了——你是真的人。天啊～～"
"。这地方烂透了～～。谁都信不过！跟老家一模一样～～。”它叹了口气，你这才转回身"
"。“听着，我们真得赶紧离开这儿～～。你要是需要什么，我尽量快～～。快点～～。拜"
"托～～。我……受够……这个破地方了～～……”蛞蝓族气急败坏地说完，你有一点时间可以在"
"舰船上购物或者做点别的事。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:704
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUGPARANOIA_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_ALIGNED\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:708
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUGPARANOIA_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_ALIGNED\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:714
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUGPARANOIA_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_ALIGNED\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "顺着蛞蝓族的意，转过身去。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:716
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUGPARANOIA_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_ALIGNED\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你转过身，屏幕里的蛞蝓族立刻尖叫起来：“我就知道～～！你骗不了我～～，僵尸杂碎"
"～～！去死吧～～！”它立刻切断通讯，武器开始充能。你用布擦了擦后背……看来之前你"
"那名受灵魂瘟疫影响的船员把一些黏液沾到了你背上。糟了……好吧，准备战斗！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:719
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUGPARANOIA_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_ALIGNED\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:725
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUGPARANOIA_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "我不转身。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:727
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUGPARANOIA_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你站在原地一动不动，十分坚定。蛞蝓族尖叫起来～～：“僵尸就会这么说～～！你骗不"
"了我～～，僵尸杂碎～～！去死吧～～！”它切断通讯，武器开始启动……你真的看起来很"
"像僵尸吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:730
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUGPARANOIA_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:738
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUGPARANOIA_REAL\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "因为这些蛞蝓族太烦人了，攻击他们。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:740
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUGPARANOIA_REAL\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "说实话，你把这些狂发通讯的家伙解决掉，等于是在帮这个星域一个忙。他们一察觉到"
"你的攻击意图，通讯请求立刻停止，武器全部启动！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:743
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUGPARANOIA_REAL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:749
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUGPARANOIA_REAL\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "无视这些蛞蝓族没完没了的骚扰通讯。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:751
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUGPARANOIA_REAL\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你很满足于无视这些蛞蝓族、只管自己的事，但他们似乎另有打算……发现你无视他们的"
"通讯后，他们的武器开始启动，并准备发起攻击！你不确定这从一开始就是个陷阱，还"
"是他们只是太过多疑，但无论如何，你都已准备好自卫。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:754
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUGPARANOIA_REAL\"]/choice[3]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:769
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SCAREDDEEPONE_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "那艘船四分五裂，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:772
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SCAREDDEEPONE_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:777
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SCAREDDEEPONE_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr "敌方船员尽数死亡，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:780
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SCAREDDEEPONE_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:787
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SCAREDDEEPONE_FIGHT_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr "击败深渊潜者后，你的灵魂隐隐作痛……真的只能这样吗？是的。只能如此。至少你会这"
"样告诉自己，哪怕只是为了让自己心里好受一点。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:791
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SCAREDDEEPONE_ECSTATIC\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"……深渊潜者们欣喜若狂。他们围绕着它，跳起了某种仪式之舞：\n"
"\n"
"“我们……得救了！我们得救了！”\n"
"“黑暗之神的行事……果然高深莫测！”\n"
"“这一切……都是它早已注定的旨意！”\n"
"\n"
"最终，之前和你对话的那只深渊潜者转向另外两只：“我和其他族人……将带着这份恩惠……"
"返回故乡。我恳请……你们两位护送主上的使者……穿过这片荒原。”两只深渊潜者点了点头"
"，对方转而对你说道：“我会留下……部分族人，以及……我们能筹集到的所有物资。如果愿"
"意……请随意交易。我们……永远感激您，联邦大人。”说完，最先开口的那只深渊潜者迈步"
"走了过来……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:800
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SCAREDDEEPONE_ECSTATIC\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:802
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SCAREDDEEPONE_ECSTATIC\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……接着是第二只……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:805
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SCAREDDEEPONE_ECSTATIC\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:807
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SCAREDDEEPONE_ECSTATIC\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……然后拿出了他们认为能拿出的所有物资。当那两只深渊潜者与你的船员互相认识时，"
"其他的深渊潜者则恳请你浏览他们剩下的物资。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:810
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SCAREDDEEPONE_ECSTATIC\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "那我们就来采购吧！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:824
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SCAREDDEEPONE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你被商店信标吸引，进入星云的一片空旷区域，眼前出现了一艘深渊潜者的飞船。你不"
"确定它是否已被物质病毒感染，于是在远处观察它的动向，而对方似乎也同样对你保持"
"着警惕。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:827
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SCAREDDEEPONE\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "尝试与这艘飞船通讯。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:829
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SCAREDDEEPONE\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "你成功接通了通讯，当屏幕里出现一只活生生的深渊潜者时，你心中的焦虑一扫而空。“"
"联邦……在这里？这么说信标……起效了？我们……得救了吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:831
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SCAREDDEEPONE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "得救？我该做些什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:833
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SCAREDDEEPONE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"深渊潜者局促地动了动：“我们……已经缺少原材料……很久了。平日里……我们自认是……利用"
"废弃旧物资的行家，可是……这场灵魂瘟疫的肆虐……几乎毁掉了一切。我们……想尽快离开"
"，但是……缺少旅途所需的物资。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:835
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SCAREDDEEPONE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你们当初为什么会来到这里？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:837
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SCAREDDEEPONE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"它们的神态又变了，但这次不是局促，而是戒备，甚至有些隐秘。“那……用不着你操心。"
"我们……来这里自有原因。来到这个……该死的地方……”一阵令人难受的沉默过后，深渊潜者"
"清了清嗓子继续说道：“所以……你到底想不想交易？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:839
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SCAREDDEEPONE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DEEPONES\"]/text"
msgstr "(深渊潜者船员) 同族……你有心事。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:841
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SCAREDDEEPONE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DEEPONES\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你看着这只深渊潜者不断变换姿态与神情，就像在游戏里疯狂刷表情一样。它们听到你"
"的深渊潜者开口，肩膀瞬间垮下，立刻失去了镇定：“同族……在这里？竟然……在联邦的飞"
