"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESCUESHELL_FIGHT_WIN_SHELL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"甲壳族发出一声低沉又烦躁的叹息，不过你明白这并非针对你，“说的应该是阿尔科莱。"
"这家伙混蛋得很，却在区里一手遮天。让他不爽的是，出了这片区域他就没这么大权力"
"了，我猜伊普西隆当初会来这里，就是因为这个。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1274
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESCUESHELL_FIGHT_WIN_SHELL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_alkali\"]/text"
msgstr "（阿尔科莱）“你说他是个彻头彻尾的混蛋？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1276
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESCUESHELL_FIGHT_WIN_SHELL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_alkali\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"阿尔科莱从你身后慢悠悠地靠了过来，那名甲壳族见状吓得连连后退：“长、长、长官？"
"！您怎么会在这里？！难道说……您特地让这些联邦军官一路护送到这里，就为了找我？”"
"阿尔科莱嗤笑一声：“找你？我连你名字都不知道。不过等这堆烂事了结之后，我肯定会"
"知道的。我要是你，现在就赶紧把履历擦干净；还好我不是你！”他大笑着转身离开，只"
"留下那名甲壳族，神情彻底沮丧了下去……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1278
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESCUESHELL_FIGHT_WIN_SHELL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_alkali\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你要知道……联邦这边一直都在招人。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1280
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESCUESHELL_FIGHT_WIN_SHELL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_alkali\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他们靠了过来，听到这话立刻精神一振：“你是……在暗示我心里想的那件事吗？”你点了"
"点头，甲壳族重重松了口气：“那我就和阿尔科莱平起平坐了，对吧？至少在他上船这段"
"时间是。他绝对会气死的。”他们窃笑起来，和刚才阿尔科莱的笑声如出一辙：“让他嚣"
"张。混蛋。不过我过去的时候，你尽管和我的同伴交易就行！”甲壳族转身驶出房间，片"
"刻之后就出现在了你的飞船上……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1283
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESCUESHELL_FIGHT_WIN_SHELL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_alkali\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "好啊，去你的阿尔科莱！商店时间到！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1285
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESCUESHELL_FIGHT_WIN_SHELL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_alkali\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……这时一个新角色走了进来，手里拿着一份商品目录。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1288
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESCUESHELL_FIGHT_WIN_SHELL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_alkali\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1298
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESCUESHELL_FIGHT_WIN_SHELL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "这位伊普西隆……你之前说过他已经失联了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1300
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESCUESHELL_FIGHT_WIN_SHELL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“是啊……这实在是个谜，就算在那些顶尖学者当中也没人清楚。伊普西隆实验室及其成员"
"在负责人与首领闹翻后，脱离了科学区的管控，一路来到这里秘密进行研究。可没过多"
"久他们就彻底失联了……那都是好几年前的事了，剩下的你也看到了。他们就这么凭空消"
"失了。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1302
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESCUESHELL_FIGHT_WIN_SHELL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "他们到底在研究什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1304
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESCUESHELL_FIGHT_WIN_SHELL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"甲壳族微微收紧了身体，和我们大多数人研究的是同一样东西，我向你保证。不过我不"
"能……确切告诉你那是什么。这是怪才体的商业机密之类的。一阵尴尬的沉默过后，甲壳"
"族又精神起来，好了！不说这个了！在我离开之前，你有什么需要的吗？甲壳族向后退"
"去，展示出他们的存货，你可以进行交易了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1307
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESCUESHELL_FIGHT_WIN_SHELL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1319
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESCUESHELL_FIGHT_WIN_SHELL\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "关于那个商店信标……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1321
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESCUESHELL_FIGHT_WIN_SHELL\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "甲壳族精神一振，“是啊！在我赶紧离开这儿之前，我能给你提供点东西。看看吧！”甲"
"壳族向后退去，展示出他们的存货，你可以进行交易了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1324
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESCUESHELL_FIGHT_WIN_SHELL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1332
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESCUESHELL_FIGHT_WIN_HUSKS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你驶过躯壳族飞船的残骸，立刻向附近的甲壳族发送通讯信号，但在这么做的时候你察"
"觉到有些不对劲……他们的飞船同样在毫无规律地移动。如果这些怪物能做出这种事，那"
"这个商店信标肯定是个陷阱……或者只是飞船前主人留下的东西。你竭尽全力逃离，但还"
"是有部分躯壳族强行登上了你的飞船！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1341
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESCUESHELL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你抵达商店信标时，一艘飞船从你身旁飞驰而过，你认出了它那近乎毫无规律的移动方"
"式……而且，你认出了它的目标！一艘满载躯壳的飞船正径直冲向前面的甲壳族飞船！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1343
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESCUESHELL\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "介入。保护商人！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1345
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESCUESHELL\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "你冲到布满躯壳的飞船前方，在它曲折行进时占据了先机，并准备阻止它前进！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1348
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESCUESHELL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1354
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESCUESHELL\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "任由甲壳族自生自灭。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1356
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESCUESHELL\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "你并不想卷入这场战斗。尽管心中不忍，你还是转身离开甲壳族，假装对他们的困境一"
"无所知。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1358
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESCUESHELL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
