msgstr "……它冒着泡，愤怒地蠕动着，随后钻入你的舰体，汇聚成一群灵魂瘟疫躯壳！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1416
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SWARMPRIZE_NAVIGATEGAMBLE_SUCCESS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你竭尽全力在外面的灵魂瘟疫黏液中机动操控，令你惊讶的是，你成功抵达了储藏点，"
