#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1607
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP_FIRSTGAMBLE_SUCCESS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"没错，你顺利收集到了大量无人争抢的废料。然而，外面新的微光吸引了你的注意，你"
"意识到外面的一些残骸终究还是被感染了……如果你再继续收集，可能就是在碰运气了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1610
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP_FIRSTGAMBLE_SUCCESS\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "不会有事的。继续前进！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1614
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP_FIRSTGAMBLE_SUCCESS\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我们别太贪心了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1616
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP_FIRSTGAMBLE_SUCCESS\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "你决定最好还是避免遭遇更多灵魂瘟疫躯壳的风险，不再触碰剩余的残骸。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1622
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP_FIRSTGAMBLE_FAILURE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你刚一开始收集外面的废料……就因为太过仓促而意识到自己犯了错。被碰到的第一块废"
"料疯狂扭动，带着虹彩的触须向外伸展，将其余残骸甩进星云之中；紧接着，它对你的"
"舰体发动攻击，显露出自始至终都是由灵魂瘟疫躯壳融化聚合而成的真身！看来这并不"
"是你所期待的收获……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1627
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP_SECONDGAMBLE_SUCCESS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"看来你并不算倒霉，你继续填满自己的金库，成功没有惊动外面任何被灵魂瘟疫感染的"
"物质。剩余的废料还有很多，但在此多留片刻，不仅要冒着潜伏的灵魂瘟疫躯壳发怒的"
"风险，还要面对叛军舰队的威胁……你会怎么做？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1630
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP_SECONDGAMBLE_SUCCESS\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "我生来就是为了冒险！继续！前进！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1634
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP_SECONDGAMBLE_SUCCESS\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "够了。我准备离开这里。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1636
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP_SECONDGAMBLE_SUCCESS\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "你决定最好避免同时面对灵魂瘟疫躯壳与叛军的风险，不再触碰剩余的残骸。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1642
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP_SECONDGAMBLE_FAILURE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"这次你就没那么幸运了……你试图继续收集外面的废料，可其中一块在被触碰时突然扭动"
"起来，带着虹彩的触须向外伸展，将其余残骸甩进星云；紧接着，它对你的舰体发动攻"
"击，显露出自始至终都是由灵魂瘟疫躯壳融化聚合而成的形态！你说不上惊讶，但这依"
"旧是件倒霉事……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1647
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP_THIRDGAMBLE_SUCCESS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"一段时间过去，你意识到自己成功了……你把这鬼地方搜刮得一干二净。外面剩下的只有"
"那些看起来被感染的残骸，而你还没那么贪心。或者说……你真的不贪心吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1651
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP_THIRDGAMBLE_SUCCESS\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "我当然有那么贪心。把废料都拿走！全部都拿走！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1653
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP_THIRDGAMBLE_SUCCESS\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"还没等任何人阻止你，你就操控舰船去收集外面那些被灵魂瘟疫感染的废料……可废料一"
"被触碰就开始扭动，泛着虹彩的触须向外伸展，同时惊动了其他碎片，它们也做出了同"
"样的反应。你彻底激怒了一整群灵魂瘟疫躯壳！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1658
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP_THIRDGAMBLE_SUCCESS\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我或许贪心，但如果命都没了，废料还有什么用？别去碰那些被感染的物质。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1660
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP_THIRDGAMBLE_SUCCESS\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "带着它毫无意义，对吧？对吧……？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1662
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP_THIRDGAMBLE_SUCCESS\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "对吧？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1664
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP_THIRDGAMBLE_SUCCESS\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……收下它吧……没错……带上我们……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1667
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP_THIRDGAMBLE_SUCCESS\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "好吧……我收下它……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1669
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP_THIRDGAMBLE_SUCCESS\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"就在你即将碰到外面那块被灵魂瘟疫感染的废料前，你猛地从恍惚中惊醒。刚才那是怎"
"么回事？你感觉……有什么东西在你脑海里低语，引诱着你放纵内心的贪婪……你是要疯了"
"吗？至少你及时回过神来。在准备从信标跃迁离开时，那些低语再也没有出现，这让你"
"心有余悸。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1679
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP_THIRDGAMBLE_FAILURE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"这次你可没那么走运了，你试图继续收集外面的废料，可其中一块刚被触碰就剧烈扭动"
"起来，泛着虹彩的触须向外伸展，同时惊动了其他碎片，它们也跟着扭动不止，你不仅"
"激怒了一整群灵魂瘟疫躯壳，就连叛军也正在逼近，外面那些未被污染的剩余废料被狠"
"狠抽飞，向着星云更深处散去，该死。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1685
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP\"]/text"
msgstr "你瞥见外面的太空中有什么东西在闪烁，你本以为那不过是又一块被灵魂瘟疫感染的物"
"质……可你很快意识到，这远不止如此。这里竟然是一整片残骸区域！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1688
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP\"]/choice[@req=\"SCRAP_COLLECTOR\"]/text"
msgstr "（废料收集臂）太棒了。咱们这次好好收一波废料！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1692
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP\"]/choice[@req=\"MAGNET_ARM\"]/text"
msgstr "（磁性回收臂）太棒了，咱们这次真的要大收一波废料！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1696
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "噢，太棒了！咱们来收点废料！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1700
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP\"]/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "哦，绝对不行！别碰那些废料。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1702
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP\"]/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你并不信任这片残骸区……在这个星域，此刻还有什么东西没有被物质病毒腐蚀？你不愿"
"为了一点微不足道的废料，拿舰上所有人的生命冒险，于是尽量不去触碰这些残骸。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1704
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1708
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_RISKYSCRAP\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1734
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_GHOSTRESCUE_GHOSTABOARD_TRUEGHOST\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"等你靠近它们时，这名魂灵族纵身一跃，穿透气闸进入舰内。它稍作平复后解释，自己"
"被困在这里最多也就几天。显然，一场由灵魂瘟疫物质病毒引发的感染已在它的飞船上"
"肆虐，慢慢腐蚀着飞船与舰上的魂灵族。这名魂灵族在事态恶化前选择离开，从此便一"
"直在星云中漂流……直到现在！它对你心怀感激，主动提出加入你的船员队伍，与你一同"
"逃离这片疯狂之地。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1739
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_GHOSTRESCUE_GHOSTABOARD_HUSKGHOST\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"等你足够靠近它们时，这名魂灵族纵身一跃，穿透气闸进入舰内。可它刚登舰，气态的"
"身躯就开始……扭曲。蒸发。你惊恐地看着这名魂灵族在你面前死去，五颜六色的粒子在"
"它刚才站立的地方开始凝聚。这些粒子一边形成一边落在地上，最终汇成一滩你认得出"
"来的、被灵魂瘟疫感染的物质。从这滩物质中升起了一具灵魂瘟疫躯壳，它的模样正是"
"刚刚死去的魂灵族的扭曲复刻。它就站在那里，而你该行动了……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1742
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_GHOSTRESCUE_GHOSTABOARD_HUSKGHOST\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "先动手！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1744
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_GHOSTRESCUE_GHOSTABOARD_HUSKGHOST\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "你朝这具躯壳射击，它的身体扭曲变形躲开了攻击……看来你激怒了它！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1749
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_GHOSTRESCUE_GHOSTABOARD_HUSKGHOST\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "等着这具躯壳先行动。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1751
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_GHOSTRESCUE_GHOSTABOARD_HUSKGHOST\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你迟疑着没有先动手，只是等待着，那具躯壳就只是站在那里。最后，它发出一阵奇怪"
"的、咕噜咕噜的声响，然后转身走进了另一个房间……你的船员们都纷纷避开它的路线，"
"但它看起来对他们也毫无兴趣。那么，这是一只友好的躯壳吗？你那位新长着触须的同"
"伴把一把勺子整个吞进了躯干里，你不禁开始疑惑，到底是什么原因让这些怪物中有的"
"变得温顺又容易受影响。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1758
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_GHOSTRESCUE_GHOSTABOARD_EVILHUSK\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"等你足够靠近它们时，你以为这名魂灵族会纵身一跃，可它却只是……站在那里。你还没"
"反应过来，它脚下的金属圆盘就炸开成一团五颜六色的灵魂瘟疫感染物质，当场杀死了"
"这名魂灵族，虹色的黏液溅在你的船体外壳上。这些物质很快就渗透进来，凝聚成灵魂"
"瘟疫躯壳，开始发起攻击！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1763
