msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTHREE\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "是的，你闭上双眼……只觉得一无所求。除了这份已然降临的升华，你还需要什么呢？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2382
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTHREE\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "升华……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2384
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTHREE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你意识到，这些都是别人的欲望。你从来都不想升华，也不想要这类愚蠢的东西。不，"
"你更感兴趣的是……实际的利益。是能将胆敢挡在你面前的一切夷为平地的武器。对，这"
"样就够了……那就这么做吧。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2386
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTHREE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "那就让它实现吧……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2388
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTHREE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"当你的飞船驶入信标时，你醒了过来，意识到启动超光速引擎时，你肯定是昏过去了一"
"会儿。你身旁有一件奇怪的物体，通体漆黑，触感灼热，你内心深处莫名明白，这是一"
"件武器……它散发出的热量令人沉醉。没错，这就是你一直想要的一切。窗外空旷的星云"
"微微闪烁；你觉得，它也在表示赞同。在超光速引擎充能期间，你要做些什么，还是只"
"是呆呆地看着你这件新武器？它确实值得这般倾慕……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2392
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTHREE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2396
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTHREE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2408
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTWO\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"走出房间，来到走廊，再向飞船深处走去，便进入了一间比之前大得多的中央房间，但"
"里面仍摆满了类似的物品。不过，旁边一张桌子上的某样东西确实引起了你的注意……像"
"是一本日记；虽有破损，但仍完好到足以让你翻阅一番。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2410
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTWO\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "检查这本日记。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2412
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTWO\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"这本日记的皮质装订页就算状况最好的地方也已破烂不堪，最糟的部分则要么被撕掉，"
"要么完全无法辨认。不过你还是很庆幸还有能读懂的内容；书的封面上潦草写着两个词"
"：愚者。这里似乎曾经写过别的文字，但后来被彻底刮掉并涂改掉了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2414
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTWO\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "有意思……把能看清的页面都读一遍。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2416
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTWO\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你翻到第一页能看清的页面，阅读上面的内容：\n"
"\n"
"———的日志，第13天\n"
"愚者\n"
"\n"
"自从伊普西隆离开———以来，已经过去了近两周，担忧日益加剧。我已尽力平息这些流言"
"，但我的部下———深入星云之中。但愿我们都能继续———\n"
"\n"
"页面剩余部分已无法辨认。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2425
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTWO\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "翻到下一页。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2427
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTWO\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你翻到下一页尚能辨认的文字：\n"
"\n"
"————日志，第47天\n"
"愚者\n"
"\n"
"今天实验室又一次险酿大祸。在一次——实验对象的常规操作中，——不慎跌入了它的容器"
"，——被迫启动疏散程序，值班军官立刻冲进来将两者分开。在——之后，她的甲壳裂开，"
"下方的韧带也被——撕裂。所幸她最终活了下来，但在剩下的——施压之下，我们实在不能"
"如此粗心。我必须提醒——\n"
"\n"
"这一页的其余内容已无法辨认。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2436
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTWO\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "翻到下一页。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2438
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTWO\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你翻到下一页有可辨认文字的页面：\n"
"\n"
"——————第52天\n"
"愚者\n"
"\n"
"——状况进一步恶化。她处理听觉与视觉指令的能力在——内迅速衰退，运动功能——。我们"
"对——的安全已经无法再抱有更多顾虑。我下令将空间站重新部署，深入到——异常信号区"
"域。如果我们不能——，我担心其存续时间——。\n"
"\n"
"不过也并非全是坏消息，因为——出现了一个有趣的进展。我们回收了一件奇怪的造物，"
"它正漂浮穿过——\n"
"\n"
"这一页的剩余内容已无法辨认。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2447
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTWO\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "翻到下一页。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2449
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTWO\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你翻到下一页尚能辨认的文字：\n"
"\n"
"——的日志，第54天\n"
"愚者\n"
"\n"
"令——惊讶的是，她几乎奇迹般地恢复了。她能行动、进食，——在社交上仍有些困难，但"
"考虑到——仍受幻听困扰，这也在意料之中。她曾与死亡如此接近，我——。就今天的实验"
"而言，我认为它成功了！——已成功融合，与实验对象呈现出相似形态，并对——作出反应—"
"—\n"
"\n"
"这一页的剩余内容已无法辨认。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2458
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTWO\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "翻到下一页。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2460
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTWO\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你翻到下一页尚能辨认的文字：\n"
"\n"
"——的日志，——\n"
"愚者\n"
"\n"
"——也一样。无法辨别它的来源，也无法确定它是否与我们——的那件造物有关。这声音很"
"难被忽视，但没有任何确切证据表明这些低语只是某种——的副作用。这影响了我下属的"
"士气。为了走到这一步，我们已经遭遇了无数挫折，我们再也浪费不起更多——在这个区"
"域了。我不会允许——仅仅为了争取一点时间就这么做。为什么那些——必须\n"
"\n"
"这一页的剩余内容已无法辨认。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2469
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTWO\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "翻到下一页。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2471
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTWO\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你翻到下一页尚能辨认的文字：\n"
"\n"
"——————2\n"
"愚者\n"
"\n"
"——越来越响，越来越响，越来越响，而我感觉——不断深入，直到找到它的源头。仓促行"
"事并不理想，但我们——渴望安宁与平静。考虑到我们精神的不稳定性，已经很难维持——"
"对实验对象的嘲弄。我必须在——中压过这些噪音，确保——获得自由，至少作为临时措施"
"。希望这能为我们争取到足够的时间，抵达——\n"
"\n"
"这一页的剩余内容已无法辨认。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2480
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTWO\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "翻到下一页。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2482
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTWO\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你翻到下一页尚能辨认的文字：\n"
"\n"
"——————4\n"
"愚者\n"
"\n"
"——这里什么都没有。我自己仍难以相信。我带领着所有人——，那些信任我的人，可结果"
"呢？有什么东西潜入了我们的意识，我的一些同伴已经——。到底是为了什么？阿尔科莱"
"一直都是对的吗？我难道只是个——。明天的实验要采取措施。我绝不允许我们空手而归"
"。在经历了这一切之后——。我今晚睡不着，那些——无比响亮。就像我身体的每一部分都"
"在尖叫着要我成功。我发誓，如果真的有更高的力量，我愿意——任何代价。任何代价。"
"求你——\n"
"\n"
"这一页的剩余内容已无法辨认。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2491
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTWO\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "翻到下一页。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2493
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTWO\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你翻完日记剩下的部分，发现后面全是空白。你在思索作者的命运时，心里一阵发沉……"
"这里到底发生了什么？飞船残骸冰冷死寂的墙壁没有给出任何确切答案，而你除了继续"
"探索，也别无选择。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2496
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTWO\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "合上书本，前往下一个房间。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2516
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTWO\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "没兴趣。把书放回去。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2518
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTWO\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "你的时间太过宝贵，不该浪费在读一本不知是谁的甲壳族日记上。把书放回原处后，这"
"个房间已经没什么可做的了……是时候继续往深处走了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2520
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE_PARTTWO\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "前往下一个房间。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2530
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE\"]/text"
msgstr "你从船体上的破口进入残骸内部，探索就此开始。入口处散落着成堆的实验设备：破碎"
"的烧杯、撕烂的笔记，以及功能不明、破旧不堪的复杂机械。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2532
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "检查这些破碎的烧杯。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2534
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"这些烧杯里曾经装着的化学物质早就没了。从飞船现在平静漂浮在太空的状态来看，应"
"该是在乘员离开之前，它们就已经碎裂了。而且这个房间还算整齐，说明不是突然剧烈"
"失压，而是在很长一段时间里慢慢漏气。对于甲壳族这种完全依赖飞船内部气体安全生"
"存的种族来说，这意味着飞船很可能在损坏前就被主动遗弃在这里了。但到底是为了什"
"么？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2536
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "有意思……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2542
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "检查那些被撕烂的笔记。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2544
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"这些笔记有的被撕碎，有的残破不堪，散落在房间各处。它们用一种你和你的翻译器都"
"无法识别的外星文字书写，你仅能辨认出其中包含着某种数学公式……还有形态怪异、无"
"定形的生物图示。你发现，每一张保存完好、能看到右下角的笔记都盖着同一个印记，"
"而印记上的刻字你可以辨认：伊普西隆。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2546
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "有意思……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2552
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "检查这些复杂的机器。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2554
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"一眼无法确定这些机器的用途，但它们的内部和外部组件都遭到了严重损坏。有意思的"
"是，房间里的其他东西并没有受到这么严重的破坏，而且在太空真空环境中也几乎没有"
"自然损耗的痕迹……这说明，出于某种原因，这些机器在飞船被遗弃之前就被人故意破坏"
"了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2556
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES_WRECKEXPLORE\"]/choice[3]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "有意思……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2564
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"一艘甲壳族飞船在外面狂暴的星云中几乎一动不动地漂浮着，所有信号都已完全沉寂。"
"以它如今这般严重破损的程度，你能感觉到它被遗弃在这里至少已经有好几年了……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2568
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_FOOLISHNOTES\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "靠近这艘被遗弃的飞船。"

