"～，谢谢您，圣者～，但我们最好马上启程。再见～～！”他们伸手按下按钮，结束了通"
"讯……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3392
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "等等！我们就不能谈谈吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3394
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "通灵者的动作猛地停下，注意力重新转向你：“嗯？变元者～～是靠闲聊领薪水的吗？你"
"想干什么？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3396
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "主要是想知道答案。通灵会在这里做什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3398
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "“我们来这儿是，呃……有事～～。这个回答你满意～～吗？”毫不夸张地说，他们看起来"
"急于离开。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3400
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_SLUG\"]/text"
msgstr "（蛞蝓族船员）“我可是乖乖假装交税～～的，该死！回答这该死的问题～～！”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3402
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_SLUG\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"通灵者正对你的蛞蝓族逃税的事表示不满，这时另一只蛞蝓族从后面打断他们：“够了～"
"～，斯科勒姆。我来接手～～。这些联邦军看起来……还算有本事～～。”他们滑到通灵者"
"前面，你才发现这不是普通的蛞蝓族，而是蛞蝓破坏者。他们再次开口：“回答你的问题"
"～～，这些友善的蛞蝓族～～是应我请求来的，担任我的护卫～～。我差不多算是他们"
"的……赞助者～～。对～～，就这么说吧。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3404
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_SLUG\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "护卫？目的何在？这里不过是片废土。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3406
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_SLUG\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"破坏者轻轻扯了扯胡须：“在某种程度上～～，确实是这样。我原本以为这里有关于怪才"
"体的重要机密～～，但到目前为止，我们发现的只有越来越多被灵魂瘟疫感染的怪物～"
"～。为了敲诈情报赔上性命……赔上他们的性命或许可以～～，但我可不行～～。”他们身"
"后的通灵者低声嘟囔了几句，破坏者继续说道：“他们更想赌一把逃跑～～，但你看起来"
"更……有技术～～，也更能打～～。你愿意代替他们护送我吗～～？作为交换～～，我愿"
"意为你效力一段时间～～。我唯一的心愿～～就是活着离开这个鬼地方～～。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3408
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_SLUG\"]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "可以，但……通灵会怎么办？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3410
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_SLUG\"]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“嗯？哦，反正我也没给他们付钱～～。他们会来，是因为我手里有证据，证明他们把大"
"量纳税人的钱拿去赌非法的六脚马族赛事～～。”破坏者转向通灵者，举起一个装置：“"
"所有证据都在这个驱动器里～～。我们的交易到此为止～～。”他们把装置递过去，通灵"
"者开心地跳了一段蛞蝓舞，然后匆匆离开了房间。破坏者也跟着离开，片刻之后，你发"
"现他们已经传送到了你的船上！看看你到底能不能活着离开这个鬼地方吧……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3411
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_SLUG\"]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/crewMember"
msgstr "凯撒"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3415
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_SLUG\"]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我就不奉陪了。祝你一路顺风！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3417
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_SLUG\"]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "破坏者对你的回答有些失望，但还是接受了，把信标留在了通灵会的飞船上。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3425
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我……呃……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3427
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"通灵者正要再次挂断通讯，这时另一只蛞蝓从后面打断了他们：“够了～～，斯科勒姆。"
"我来接手～～。这些联邦军看起来……还算有本事～～。”他们滑到通灵者身前，你才发现"
"这不是普通的蛞蝓，而是蛞蝓破坏者。他再次开口：“回答你的问题～～，这些友善的蛞"
"蝓～～是应我请求前来，担任我的护卫～～。我差不多算是他们的……赞助者～～。对～"
"～，就这么说吧。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3429
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "护卫？目的何在？这里不过是片废土。"

