#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3442
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "破坏者对你的回答有些失望，但还是接受了，把信标留在了通灵会的飞船上。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3452
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "报酬是必须的！我可是刚救了你们的命！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3454
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "“难道说声谢谢还不够～～？联邦军校里没教过礼貌吗～～？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3456
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你明明就是只蛞蝓。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3458
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"通灵者鼓起黏糊糊的胸膛：“那你就是个种族歧视者～～！给，拿上你那愚蠢的报酬～～"
"！”他们传送过来一点点废料，然后立刻离开了信标……你真的是种族歧视者吗？这只不过"
"是个普通观察而已，蛞蝓族通常都没什么礼貌，对吧？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3465
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "小闲聊有什么问题吗……？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3467
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr "你还没得到回应，通灵者就直接挂断了通讯，只留下你一个人，连句像样的闲聊都没捞"
"着。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3473
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "什么也不说。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3475
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "没错，他们挂断通讯，朝着星云深处逃去。你也不清楚自己原本在期待什么……或许在内"
"心深处，你只是想独处罢了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3481
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_HUSK_FIGHT_FAIL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"他们的求救信标离线了，你很清楚，以通灵会飞船现在的领先距离，你再也找不到他们"
"了。更糟的是，躯壳船也跃迁离开了，似乎对你失去了兴趣……又或者，他们只是在追通"
"灵会？你不确定躯壳是否有这样的目的性，但事实就是——你被独自留下了……而且一无所"
"获。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3496
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_CLAIRVOYANT_FIGHT_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr "如果几个世纪前的原始通灵者能看到他们的后代现在倒在像你这样的船上，他们会哭泣的。坦率地说，你并不介意这一点。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3499
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_CLAIRVOYANT_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3501
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_CLAIRVOYANT_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "似乎精英蛞蝓族船的货物在战斗中幸存下来。里面有一件完好的武器，你把它带回星舰。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3504
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_CLAIRVOYANT_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3506
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED_CLAIRVOYANT_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"收好所有东西，你才发现已经很久没看见那艘躯壳船了……还没等你做出反应，它就猛地"
"掠了过去！如同丧尸般的船员纷纷弃船，直接登了上来！看来你刚才实在是太放松警惕"
"了……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3516
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你发现求救信标来自一只蛞蝓通灵者，他们的飞船在星云云雾间疾速穿梭，另一艘飞船"
"紧随其后，追得很紧……他们肯定是被躯壳追杀了。通灵者向来对联邦不算友好，但你不"
"确定，就这么放任他们自生自灭，自己心里是否过得去……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3519
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_nights\"]/text"
msgstr "（七夜）“哈，活该～～！”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3521
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_nights\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"（七夜）仰头灌下一整瓶，“咚”地把空瓶砸在地上，举起一条触手，姿态充满挑衅意味"
"：“你们那些愚蠢的规矩在这儿屁用没有，对吧？这里可是海盗的地盘，蠢货们！”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3523
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_nights\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "呃……那你的骑士们在哪呢，七夜？要说这是谁的地盘，怎么看都像是躯壳的地盘。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3525
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_nights\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他盯着你看了一会儿，在刚碎的玻璃渣里不安地扭动着身体：“那……呃……你的联邦朋友们"
"又在哪呢，嗯？真出了事可没见你呼叫他们。还有，别跟我讲什么丧尸大道理；我可是"
"混过政坛的！”七夜烦躁地醉醺醺爬走了，大概是去找另一瓶酒，你的注意力也重新回到"
"了外面那两艘飞船上。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3527
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_CLAIRVOYANTGREED\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_nights\"]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "救下通灵者飞船。"

