"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_FIGHT_WIN_GUARDIAN\"]/text"
msgstr "到这个时候，你本该预料到躯壳会发动突袭，但你仍然因为这片区域里没有谁能完全信"
"任这一点而感到不安。不过，说到这片区域里的人……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3650
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_FIGHT_WIN_GUARDIAN\"]/choice[@req=\"shell_guardian\""
" and not(@lvl)]/text"
