"其他人，我唯一的选择就只有保持安静……直到你找到我。剩下的事，你都知道了……”科学"
"家叹了口气，目光转向了别处……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3698
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_FIGHT_WIN_SCIENTIST\"]/choice[@req=\"shell_scientist\""
" and not(@lvl)]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "那真是……太可怕了。我很抱歉。如果你愿意，欢迎留在舰上。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3700
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_FIGHT_WIN_SCIENTIST\"]/choice[@req=\"shell_scientist\""
" and not(@lvl)]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他们的注意力重新回到你身上，点了点头，“我根本没有别的地方可去，就算我想……我只"
"希望他们当初听我的，我们在某个联邦星域躲上一段时间就好了。我现在唯一能期盼的"
"，就是也许有一天，这场战争会结束，我仍然能带着热烈的欢迎回到怪才体……”的确，那"
"听起来很美好。或许有一天，联邦自身的战争也会结束，你也能迎来同样的安宁。不管"
"怎样，这都是一个值得为之奋战的理想。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3706
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_FIGHT_WIN_SCIENTIST\"]/choice[@req=\"shell_scientist\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "去找那位甲壳科学家。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3708
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_FIGHT_WIN_SCIENTIST\"]/choice[@req=\"shell_scientist\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr "很遗憾，他们似乎已经在战斗中阵亡了。你或许永远都无法知道这里究竟发生了什么。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3714
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_FIGHT_WIN_HUSK\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"到这个时候，你本该预料到躯壳会发动突袭，但你仍然因为这片星域里没有任何事物能"
"完全信任而感到不安。虽然这些甲壳族为何会出现在这里的谜团或许永远无法解开，但"
"至少你安然无恙地逃了出来。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3726
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_BOARDED_STRANGESOUND_GUARDIAN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"靠近声音的来源，声音变得清晰了一些；那是一只痛苦的甲壳族发出的喘息声。你在角"
"落里找到了他们，恐慌似乎攫住了它，它的目光在天花板的不同位置慌乱地移动，艰难"
"地挤出几句话：“他们……在这……不……安全！快跑！”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3729
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_BOARDED_STRANGESOUND_GUARDIAN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "抓住那只甲壳族，快跑！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3731
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_BOARDED_STRANGESOUND_GUARDIAN\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的命令得到执行，那只甲壳族被迅速拖了回来；通讯画面里传来一阵咕噜声，来源不"
"明，你们驶出甲壳族的飞船，并急忙断开两艘飞船之间的连接。就在这时，那只甲壳族"
"恢复了些许镇定，在光亮中你能更清楚地看清它；这是一名守护者。从它们飞船的配色"
"来看并不奇怪，但怪才体的守护者会如此惊慌、如此狼狈，本身就是不祥之兆……它急忙"
"开口：\n"
"\n"
"“我们在这里不安全！他～们会——”\n"
"\n"
"飞船猛地一震，打断了甲壳族的话，你意识到另一艘飞船已经开始移动。你刚勉强断开"
"连接、拉开一点距离，它的引擎便轰然启动，随后武器系统也随之激活！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3739
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_BOARDED_STRANGESOUND_GUARDIAN\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3747
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_BOARDED_STRANGESOUND_MECHANIC\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"靠近声音的来源，声音变得清晰了一些；那是一只痛苦的甲壳族发出的喘息声。你在角"
"落里找到了他们，恐慌似乎攫住了他们，他们的目光在天花板的不同位置慌乱地移动，"
"轻声说道：“这艘飞船已经沦陷了……这里没有希望了……如果你留在这里，我们两个都会死"
"……就像……他们一样……”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3750
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_BOARDED_STRANGESOUND_MECHANIC\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "抓住那只甲壳族，快跑！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3752
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_BOARDED_STRANGESOUND_MECHANIC\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的命令得到执行，那只甲壳族被迅速拖了回来；通讯画面里传来一阵咕噜声，来源不"
"明，你们驶出甲壳族的飞船，并急忙断开两艘飞船之间的连接。就在这时，那只甲壳族"
"恢复了些许镇定，在光亮中你能更清楚地看清它；这是一名技师。考虑到两个行政区之"
"间的隔阂，这有些反常，但你已经没有时间发问了……它开口说道，语气清晰了一些：\n"
"\n"
"“这艘飞船有防御工事吗？这些怪物已经证明了它们有能力——”\n"
"\n"
"飞船猛地一震，打断了甲壳族的话，你意识到另一艘飞船已经开始移动。你刚勉强断开"
"连接、拉开一点距离，它的引擎便轰然启动，随后武器系统也随之激活！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3760
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_BOARDED_STRANGESOUND_MECHANIC\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3768
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_BOARDED_STRANGESOUND_SCIENTIST\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"靠近声音的来源，声音变得清晰了一些；那是一只痛苦的甲壳族发出的喘息声。你在角"
"落里找到了他们，恐慌似乎攫住了他们，他们的目光在天花板的不同位置慌乱地移动，"
"急忙说道：“他～们接下来就会抓到我们……他～们会抓到我们，就像抓～住其他人一样！"
"带我离开这里！”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3771
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_BOARDED_STRANGESOUND_SCIENTIST\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "抓住那只甲壳族，快跑！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3773
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_BOARDED_STRANGESOUND_SCIENTIST\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的命令得到执行，那只甲壳族被迅速拖了回来；视频通讯里传来一阵咕噜声，来源不"
"明，你们驶出甲壳族的飞船，并急忙断开两艘飞船之间的连接。就在这时，那只甲壳族"
"恢复了些许镇定，在光亮中你能更清楚地看清它；这是一名科学家。考虑到两个行政区"
"之间的隔阂，这有些反常，但你已经没有时间发问了……它开口说道，语气平静了一些："
"\n"
"\n"
"“我们必须立刻撤离信标，在他们——”\n"
"\n"
"飞船猛地一震，打断了甲壳族的话，你意识到另一艘飞船已经开始移动。你刚勉强断开"
"连接、拉开一点距离，它的引擎便轰然启动，随后武器系统也随之激活！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3781
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_BOARDED_STRANGESOUND_SCIENTIST\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3789
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_BOARDED_STRANGESOUND_HUSK\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"靠近声音的来源，声音变得清晰了一些；比你想象的要湿润一些。像是某种咕噜声……你"
"还没来得及细想，便靠近了角落里那个神秘的身影，它的人形轮廓在阴影中扭动、翻腾"
"。一声嘶吼爆发出来，真相也随之清晰：这不是别的，正是一具躯壳！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3792
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_BOARDED_STRANGESOUND_HUSK\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "快跑！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3794
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_BOARDED_STRANGESOUND_HUSK\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的命令得到执行，众人迅速往回冲刺；通讯画面中传来更多咕噜声，却无法确定其众"
"多来源，你们驶出甲壳族的飞船，并急忙断开两艘飞船之间的连接。就在这时，你自己"
"的飞船猛地一震，你意识到第二艘飞船已经开始移动。你刚勉强断开连接、拉开一点距"
"离，它的引擎便轰然启动，随后武器系统也随之激活！更糟糕的是，似乎有几具躯壳趁"
"你忙碌之际，悄悄溜进了飞船……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3798
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_BOARDED_STRANGESOUND_HUSK\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3806
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_BOARDED\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"视频通讯接通，你眼前出现了一间昏暗房间的画面……有那么一瞬间，你不知道该如何行"
"动，但随后房间角落里一阵奇怪的沙哑声响吸引了你的注意。或许这不太像是呱呱叫声"
"，更像是……呻吟？仿佛有什么东西正承受着痛苦……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3808
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_BOARDED\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "调查这奇怪的声音。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3812
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_BOARDED\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "立刻离开那里！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3814
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_BOARDED\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"不管这里发生了什么，你都绝不会让它再制造更多杀戮。众人惊慌地赶回飞船，断开与"
"甲壳族飞船的连接，然后飞到安全距离之外。这里发生的一切无疑将成为谜团，但这或"
"许对你来说反而是件好事……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3826
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_TOXINGAMBLE_SUCCESS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你的船员做好准备，你操作飞船进行机动，让他们能够登舰。你将两艘飞船对接，成功"
"把己方飞船的入口与对方飞船锁合，你的船员得以登舰；行动十分谨慎，以免对方飞船"
"的毒素涌入你的飞船。他们必须速战速决，但他们看起来有足够能力抵御这艘飞船的气"
"体侵袭。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3828
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_TOXINGAMBLE_SUCCESS\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "接通你船员的视频通讯。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3834
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_TOXINGAMBLE_FAILURE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你的船员做好准备，你操控飞船进行机动，让他们能够登舰。两艘飞船完成对接，你成"
"功将己方飞船的入口与对方飞船锁合，你的船员得以登舰；全程十分谨慎，以免对方飞"
"船的毒素涌入你的飞船。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3836
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_TOXINGAMBLE_FAILURE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "接通你船员的视频通讯。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3838
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_TOXINGAMBLE_FAILURE\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"传回的视频画面往轻了说也堪称恐怖。你的船员刚走进飞船没几步，动作就开始变得迟"
"缓，紧接着不可避免地抽搐起来。唯一值得安慰的是，他们从那时起便迅速死去……这次"
"登舰行动失败了。你必须立刻撤离。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3841
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER_TOXINGAMBLE_FAILURE\"]/choice/event/removeCrew/text"
msgstr "你可以通过克隆舱复活你的船员，但你实在不想再派任何人回去重试了。往轻了说，刚"
"才那场面……实在太令人不适。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3849
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"军方辖区正处于罢工状态，怪才体的军用舰船极少会在自家星域内随意出没，更不用说"
"出现在这片荒芜的废弃区域了。可此刻偏偏就有一艘停在这里，状态还算完好……但在你"
"抵达后，对方既没有移动，也没有发出任何联络信号。考虑到那枚求救信标，这一切都"
"令人不安……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3853
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "看起来足够可信。联络这艘飞船。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3855
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "你尝试联络这艘甲壳族飞船，但没有得到任何回应。又试了几次，依然毫无变化；通讯"
"完全静默。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3857
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "我们登舰过去看看吧？他们也许需要帮助……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3859
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "抛开好意不谈，你很清楚，你试图登舰的依然是一艘甲壳族飞船。你需要一名能够抵御"
"飞船毒气的船员，否则你就是在白白葬送生命。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3861
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_SHELL\"]/text"
msgstr "（甲壳族船员）让你的甲壳族成员登舰。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3863
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_SHELL\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的甲壳族点了点它们的甲壳，你操控飞船进行机动，让它能够登舰。两艘飞船完成对"
"接，你成功将己方飞船的入口与对方飞船锁合，你的甲壳族成员顺利登舰；全程十分谨"
"慎，以免对方飞船的毒素涌入你的飞船。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3865
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_SHELL\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "接通你甲壳族船员的视频通讯。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3871
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_NO2\"]/text"
msgstr "（厌氧船员）让你的厌氧船员登舰。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3873
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_NO2\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他们必须动作迅速，以免吸入更多毒素，你操控飞船进行机动，让船员得以登舰。两艘"
"飞船完成对接，你成功将己方飞船的入口与对方飞船锁合，船员顺利登舰；全程十分谨"
"慎，防止对方飞船的毒素涌入你的飞船。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3875
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_NO2\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "接通你船员的视频通讯。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3881
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"DRONE_CONTROL_BOARDING\"]/text"
msgstr "（登舰无人机）让你的无人机登舰。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3883
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"DRONE_CONTROL_BOARDING\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的无人机嗡鸣着启动，你操控飞船进行机动，让它在不破坏甲壳族船体的情况下登舰"
"。两艘飞船完成对接，你成功将己方飞船的入口与对方飞船锁合，你的无人机得以登舰"
"；全程十分谨慎，以免对方飞船的毒素涌入你的飞船。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3885
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"DRONE_CONTROL_BOARDING\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "接通你无人机的视频信号。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3891
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CHECK_ANY_CREW\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "我们必须试一试，即使要冒着生命危险。让一名船员登舰。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3895
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CHECK_ANY_CREW\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "看来你已经没有船员可以派遣了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3899
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[6]/text"
msgstr "算了，我们冒不起这个险。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3901
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[6]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"整件事都透着蹊跷，而且你很清楚，这艘甲壳族飞船的毒素之外，还可能潜伏着其他未"
"知危险，你根本承受不起贸然闯入的代价。尽管心有不甘，你还是觉得必须暂且不去理"
"会这艘飞船，静待时机跃迁离开。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3903
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[6]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3907
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[6]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3915
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我知道怎么引起他们的注意。攻击！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3917
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"即便你对他们发起攻击，甲壳族也没有做出任何自卫行动。这很奇怪，毕竟他们的飞船"
"仍在供能，但你意识到，你从一开始就已经来不及拯救他们了。无论如何，你只能从他"
"们的残骸中搜刮一点残存的物资。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3921
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3923
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"就在你收集这些零碎残骸时，却突然察觉到不对劲。其中一些残骸泛着油光，还带着虹"
"彩……这艘飞船显然已经被灵魂瘟疫感染了！你还没来得及纠正打捞残骸的错误，部分废"
"料就开始渗出液体、不断冒泡，一小群躯壳猛地涌现出来，要把你变成它们的下一个猎"
"物！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3930
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "太无礼了！那我也不理他们好了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3932
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你简直要被某些外星人的厚脸皮气炸了……你把自己那无比紧急、简直是要拯救整个宇宙"
"的任务都暂时搁置，就为了回应他们的求救信号，可他们连回应你通讯的力气都拿不出"
"来？你只当是眼不见为净，不再理会那艘飞船，静静等待跃迁离开。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3934
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3938
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3946
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我不信这事儿。别管那艘飞船了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3948
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "整个星域都让你心神不宁，你绝不会再让躯壳们偷袭得手。你一刻也不信任这些甲壳族"
"。你不去理会那艘飞船，对方也没有再来骚扰，你得以安心等待跃迁离开。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3950
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3954
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLSOLDIER\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3967
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER_FIGHT_WIN_NOSHIP\"]/text"
msgstr "你必须向蛞蝓族解释他们飞船被毁的原因……至少在那之前，你可以花点时间打捞这艘飞"
"船的残骸。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3970
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER_FIGHT_WIN_NOSHIP\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "把蛞蝓族叫回来。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3972
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER_FIGHT_WIN_NOSHIP\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "自从你上次呼叫他们之后，黏液池的体积略微上涨了一些。蛞蝓族急切地回应道：“你还"
"活着！这下，你给他们点颜色看看了对吧？把他们都清理干净了？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3974
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER_FIGHT_WIN_NOSHIP\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "嗯……是这样，不过，我，呃……可能把你的飞船给毁掉了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3976
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER_FIGHT_WIN_NOSHIP\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你本以为对方会情绪激动，可蛞蝓族却异常镇定，“啊～～该死。算了～～，无所谓～～"
"。反正我之前有点撒谎，那本来就不是我的～～船，我只是搭个便车而已～～。”蛞蝓族"
"在自己的黏液里沉思了片刻，然后看向你，“对～～了，你现在有飞船对吧～～？说不定"
"……上面还有能容下我这样一个家伙的位置～～？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3978
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER_FIGHT_WIN_NOSHIP\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "呃……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3980
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER_FIGHT_WIN_NOSHIP\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他们打断了你，“太好了～～！那我就待在这儿等你赶紧过来～～！反正我也，呃，在这"
"儿做不了别的～～事～～。”你叹了口气，心想反正比这更糟的情况都有，多一个免费船"
"员也不错，于是把蛞蝓族的逃生舱接上了飞船……不过，小心那些黏液，好吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3981
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER_FIGHT_WIN_NOSHIP\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/crewMember"
msgstr "黏液领主"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3989
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER_FIGHT_WIN_NOSHIP\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "任由这只蛞蝓族自生自灭。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3991
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER_FIGHT_WIN_NOSHIP\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你实在是非常非常不擅长应对冲突。不擅长到什么程度呢——你宁愿让对方就这么待在逃"
"生舱里，泡在自己的黏液里在太空中漂流，也不愿意去跟对方说那难听的话。这就是为"
"什么你肩负着拯救宇宙的重任，而不是去做那些更难的事，比如公关……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3997
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER_FIGHT_WIN_SHIPSAVED\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"飞船上的躯壳已经清理干净，你呼叫蛞蝓族回来并告知他们消息，“～～你看，我就知道"
"我能信～～任联邦！虽说我当时也没太多，呃，选～～择。载我回我的～～船，好吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:3999
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER_FIGHT_WIN_SHIPSAVED\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "照蛞蝓族的要求去做。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4001
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER_FIGHT_WIN_SHIPSAVED\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你很顺利地找到了他们的逃生舱，没费什么力气就把他们送回了蛞蝓族的飞船。等他们"
"在里面安顿好后，再次向你通讯：“哦，～～该死～～，人都走光之后这地方也太宽敞～"
"～了吧。～～话说，你帮了我一把；我要不要也回～～报你一下？反正其他人都死了，"
"我觉得你完全可以拿走他们的一些～～东西。只是一～～些哦！蛞蝓～～也得过日子！”"
"蛞蝓族给你转了一笔相当丰厚的赏金，你发现各类资源中还藏着一件奇怪的武器……一件"
"被灵魂瘟疫物质病毒感染的武器！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4005
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER_FIGHT_WIN_SHIPSAVED\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "这是什么意思？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4007
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER_FIGHT_WIN_SHIPSAVED\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"蛞蝓族看了过去，“哦，那个？今天早上所有人都在痴迷～～那件东西。是在太空里漂着"
"发现的。好笑的是～～，这是那些僵～～尸破事爆发前我记得做的最后一件事……你不会"
"觉得这两者有关联吧？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4009
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER_FIGHT_WIN_SHIPSAVED\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "眨了几下眼睛。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4011
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER_FIGHT_WIN_SHIPSAVED\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“是啊～～，这大概只是个巧合～～。总之～～，再次谢啦！我得想想该怎么，呃，离开"
"这个地方～～……”蛞蝓族看着飞船的操控台，你估摸着它是一脸茫然，然后它随便按下一"
"个按钮，从信标处跃迁离开了。你完全相信它有本事闯出这片鬼地方。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4021
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER_FIGHT_WIN_SHIPSAVED\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "任由这只蛞蝓族自生自灭。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4023
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER_FIGHT_WIN_SHIPSAVED\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "老实说，你这个做法实在没什么道理。你就是单纯不喜欢这家伙。你一言不发地挂断了"
"通讯，花了点时间从他们的飞船上尽可能打捞些物资。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4031
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你发现一艘闲置的蛞蝓族飞船，在进入信标时收到了通讯呼叫，但你很快意识到，这通"
"呼叫并非来自飞船本身，而是来自飞船稍远一些、被星云遮挡的位置。有点奇怪……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4035
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "回应这通神秘的呼叫。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4037
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"映入你眼帘的是一幕令人极度压抑的景象，一只蛞蝓族几乎把脸贴在了屏幕上。它所在"
"的空间看起来更像是一间囚笼，四周的墙壁离它只有几英寸远，它开口说道：“谢天谢地"
"～～！我就知道我的英雄救～～星直觉不会错！我现在在逃～～生舱里，就在不远处～"
"～，那些油～～腻的混～～蛋劫持了我的飞船后，我只能想办法自保！”镜头微微移动，"
"你看到了逃生舱的下方；这只蛞蝓族几乎是泡在自己的黏液里。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4039
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你，呃……在里面待了多久了？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4041
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"蛞蝓族晃了晃镜头，“这～～重要吗？伸出你的～～触手帮帮蛞～～蝓，去解决那些东西"
"，好吗？或者，呃，用你的～～手也行！不管你有什～～么！这里太～～臭了！我一秒"
"～～都待不下去了！”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4043
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "好吧，好吧。我会把你的飞船清理干净的。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4045
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“你看～～，我一直就知道你们联邦人超棒～～！我一直都超喜欢联邦～～！”是哦……好"
"吧，不管这只蛞蝓族说得有多敷衍，你还是动身去清理他们飞船上的躯壳。就在你靠近"
"时，蛞蝓族的飞船微微一动，先是紧绷了一瞬，随即自己也紧张地靠了过来！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4048
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4054
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我能得到什么好处？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4056
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "“呃，你听～～起来跟我的前任一毛一样。我哪知道，我的谢～～谢行不行？你们这些联"
"邦～～人不就是靠爱和彩虹～～之类的东西驱动的吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4058
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "我确实挺喜欢爱与彩虹的……行吧，我干。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4060
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"它们在狭小的空间里尽力扭动着跳了段舞：“你～～看，我一直就知道你们联邦～～的人"
"超棒～～！一直都超喜欢他们！是哦……好吧，不管这只蛞蝓族态度转变得有多敷衍，你"
"还是动身去清理他们飞船上的躯壳。就在你靠近时，蛞蝓族的飞船微微一动，先是紧绷"
"了一瞬，随即自己也紧张地靠了过来！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4063
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4069
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "抱歉，我还是算了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4071
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你很难看清蛞蝓族的表情，但你能确定，在你挂断通讯时，它正被恐惧与绝望交织的情"
"绪淹没。对它们来说很不幸，但你不可能把所有人的麻烦都揽到自己身上。你得先顾好"
"你自己！你自己，还有你的……呃……船员！对！你只是个称职的船长而已！对吧？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4073
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4077
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4089
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "无视这次通讯，也无视这艘飞船。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4091
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "就算在没有噬物僵尸的星域，蛞蝓族也会让你感到不安，而你确定，这里正是布满噬物"
"僵尸的星域。这里面绝对有问题，你才不会上当！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4093
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4097
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_NAIVEEXPLORER\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4106
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_HUSK_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "那艘船四分五裂，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4109
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_HUSK_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4114
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_HUSK_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr "敌方船员尽数死亡，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4117
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_HUSK_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4124
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_HUSK_FIGHT_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"飞船的遇险信标还在运作，这让你心神不宁。你是不是就晚了一步，没能救下他们？还"
"是躯壳们把它当成诱饵故意打开的？你真希望它们没那么聪明……不过，你或许永远都无"
"法知道真相了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4135
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_LANIUS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你没花多久就精准定位到了信号的确切位置：云层中的一艘拉纽斯族飞船。你靠近时，"
"他们发来通讯：“看到求救信号吗？这里需要帮助。燃料耗尽，无法移动。需要帮忙启动"
"。”他们的引擎确实已经停机……没人知道他们已经在这里被困了多久。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4138
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_LANIUS\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "分给食铁族一些你的燃料。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4140
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_LANIUS\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你送过去几根燃料棒，食铁族的表情依旧没什么变化。不过你能看出他们心存感激，他"
"们继续说道：“这里很危险。坏金属，见过很多。坏金属会变成坏人。知道安全地点，帮"
"你指路。帮你避开坏人。”你愣了一下，随后你的导航系统收到了一份新文件……食铁族为"
"了答谢你，发来了这片星域的详细星图！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4146
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_LANIUS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "感谢他们的帮助，然后继续上路。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4148
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_LANIUS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "“多谢你。我们很快就会离开，谢谢你。”你让食铁族自行处理后续事宜，自己则准备跃"
"迁下一个信标。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4152
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_LANIUS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "问问他们一开始为什么会在这里。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4154
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_LANIUS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“本来以为这里是废弃区域，来寻找金属。结果找到了坏金属。坏金属会伤人。现在想去"
"别的地方找金属了，燃料帮了大忙。”说实话，你自己也想去别的地方找废料了……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4156
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_LANIUS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "有意思。感谢他们的帮助，然后继续上路。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4158
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_LANIUS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "“多谢你。我们很快就会离开，谢谢你。”你让食铁族自行处理后续事宜，自己则准备跃"
"迁下一个信标。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4166
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_LANIUS\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "趁他们无助的时候发动攻击。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4168
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_LANIUS\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"食铁族以目前的状态根本无力抵抗，你轻而易举地迫使他们投降了。他们心不甘情不愿"
"地按你的要求交出了所有能拿出来的东西，你的金库也因此充实了一些。好在这片荒无"
"人烟的地方，他们会把这件恶行的真相带进坟墓里……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4173
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_LANIUS\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "表示歉意，但坚持你无法提供帮助。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4175
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_LANIUS\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他们的表情没有变化，但你能听出他们语气里的失望：“没关系。也许会有其他人帮忙。"
"求救信号会一直开着。无论如何还是谢谢你。”你有些遗憾地留下食铁族自生自灭，准备"
"跃迁到下一个信标。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4181
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_ENGI\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你没花多久就精准定位到了信号的具体位置：云层中的一艘分离者飞船。你靠近时，他"
"们发来通讯：“联邦……是你吗？我们必须请求你，对我们在这里的行踪保密。你是来帮忙"
"的吗？我们的船体已经严重破损。我们可以自行修复，但已经耗尽了制造维修无人机所"
"需的零件。”他们的船体确实受损严重……没人知道他们在这里经历了多少场战斗。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4184
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_ENGI\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "把你的一些无人机零件分给半械分离者。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4186
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_ENGI\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你送过去一些无人机部件，半械分离者简短地鞠躬致谢。你能感觉到他们并不习惯这么"
"做，但依旧很感激这份帮助，他们继续说道：“我们感谢你。我们在这里看到了很多事情"
"。请允许我们与你分享。”你愣了一下，随后你的导航系统收到了一份新文件……半械分离"
"者为了答谢你，发来了这片星域的详细星图！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4192
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_ENGI\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "感谢他们的帮助，然后继续上路。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4194
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_ENGI\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "“你们太客气了，不用谢我们。祝你在这里无论做什么都好运。”你留下半械分离者自行"
"处理，准备跃迁下一个信标。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4198
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_ENGI\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "问问他们一开始为什么会在这里。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4200
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_ENGI\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他们看起来犹豫着不愿回答，茫然地凝视了片刻才终于开口：“我们来这里，是为了寻找"
"一样东西。一份足以击溃谐合势力的恩惠。可惜，这里泛滥的灵魂瘟疫躯壳完全超出了"
"我们的预料。我们认为，是时候离开了。”说实话，你自己也想赶紧离开……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4202
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_ENGI\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "有意思。感谢他们的帮助，然后继续上路。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4204
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_ENGI\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "“你们太客气了，不用谢我们。祝你在这里无论做什么都好运。”你留下半械分离者自行"
"处理，准备跃迁下一个信标。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4212
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_ENGI\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "趁他们无助的时候发动攻击。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4214
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_ENGI\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"半械分离者以目前的状态根本无力抵抗，你轻而易举就迫使他们投降了。他们心不甘情"
"不愿地按你的要求交出了所有能拿出来的东西，你的储备也因此多了一些。好在这片荒"
"无人烟的地方，他们会把你这次恶行的真相带进坟墓里……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4219
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_ENGI\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "表示歉意，但坚持你无法提供帮助。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4221
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_ENGI\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr "当你表明立场后，他们的身形微微一沉：“没关系。或许还会有其他人前来帮忙。”你有"
"些遗憾地留下半械分离者自生自灭，准备跃迁往下一个信标。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4227
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_PIRATE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你很快就精准定位到了信号的具体位置：云层中的一艘海盗船。你靠近时，他们向你喊"
"话：“变元者？你跑到这种鬼地方来干什么？别管这些了；我们刚遭遇了一群诡异的……东"
"西，那些混蛋把舰长抓走了。我真想把他们轰回他们爬出来的地狱深渊，可战斗中导弹"
"已经用光了……帮个忙？”他们的武器确实没有充能……只不过，他们的意图到底有几分真诚"
"，就不好说了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4230
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_PIRATE\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "分给海盗一些你的弹药。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4232
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_PIRATE\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你送过去几枚弹药，和你对话的海盗搓了搓手：“这才像话！嘿，这事我们会保密的。我"
"知道，帮助我们这种人可不是什么光彩事，就算你是出于好心也一样。”他摸了摸下巴，"
"似乎认真思索了一会儿，接着说道：“你知道吗，舰长肯定不会同意这么做，但他现在不"
"在这里，对吧？我可不是那种欠债不还的人。”你一时有些疑惑，随即你的导航系统收到"
"了一份新文件……作为答谢，海盗们把这片星域的详细星图发给了你！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4238
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_PIRATE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "感谢他们的帮助，然后继续上路。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4240
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_PIRATE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "“谢谢你，你这厉害的家伙！现在正是我们要好好教训那些彩虹怪人的时候。”你留下海"
"盗们自行处理，准备跳往下一个信标。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4244
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_PIRATE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "问问他们一开始为什么会在这里。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4246
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_PIRATE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"起初，舰长确信甲壳族在这里留下了值钱的东西，听上去还算是一趟有趣的差事。可"
"那是在他被人惨叫着拖出气密舱之前的事了。不过，在那之前我们已经把这片地方仔细"
"搜查过了，如果真有什么该死的秘密宝藏，那也藏得极为隐蔽。\"隐藏宝藏的可能性确"
"实十分诱人……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4248
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_PIRATE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "有意思。感谢他们的帮助，然后继续上路。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4250
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_PIRATE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "“谢谢你，你这厉害的家伙！现在正是我们要好好教训那些彩虹怪人的时候。”你留下海"
"盗们自行处理，准备跳往下一个信标。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4258
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_PIRATE\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "趁他们无助的时候发动攻击。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4260
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_PIRATE\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"海盗们以目前的状态根本无力抵抗，你轻而易举就能迫使他们投降。他们心不甘情不愿"
"地按你的要求交出所有能拿出的东西，你的库存也因此充实了些许。好在这片荒无人烟"
"的地方，他们会把你这次恶行的真相带进坟墓里……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4265
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_PIRATE\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "表示歉意，但坚持你无法提供帮助。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4267
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_PIRATE\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他们微微皱了皱眉，但还是点了点头，\"联邦本来就不该来帮我们这种混蛋。我们会想"
"出办法的。我们或许是混蛋，但绝对是够机灵的混蛋！\"至少他们士气还很高昂。你有"
"些遗憾地留下海盗们自行处理，准备跃迁往下一个信标。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4273
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_HUSK\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你没花多久就精准定位到了信号的具体位置：云层中的一艘飞船。可它的航行轨迹让你"
"觉得有些不对劲，直到你突然反应过来……这艘飞船已经被躯壳占领了！它们现在察觉到"
"了你的存在，正准备接下来攻占你的飞船！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4276
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS_SEARCHLIST_HUSK\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4283
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS\"]/text"
msgstr "根据你的星图显示，这里有一道求救信号，但你的系统侦测到其信号源仍在星云更深处"
"。你必须绕道才能找到它。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4286
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "搜寻信号源。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4290
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "别理会这个信号。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4292
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "你有自己的要务，对大海捞针般的搜寻毫无兴趣。你对这个决定感到满意，在等待超光"
"速引擎充能的过程中，身边只剩下暴风雨般的云层。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4294
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4298
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_STRANDEDGOOBERS\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4312
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SMOLDERINGREMAINS_LOOTLIST_GOODIES\"]/text"
msgstr "这里的各类战利品十分古怪，几乎是随机摆放的，但你对能抢到的所有贵重物品都感到"
"满意。将残骸搜刮一空后，除了离开信标，你别无他事可做。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4317
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SMOLDERINGREMAINS_LOOTLIST_BADDIES\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你很快发现这里几乎没有什么真正有价值的东西，大多只是一些烧焦的废料。不过你还"
"是把它们装上了飞船，随即凑近仔细观察……这是烧焦的痕迹，还是，呃……油腻的？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4320
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SMOLDERINGREMAINS_LOOTLIST_BADDIES\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "等一下！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4322
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SMOLDERINGREMAINS_LOOTLIST_BADDIES\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"这可不是普通的废料……其中一部分已经被那该死的物质病毒感染了！你还没来得及根据"
"这个发现采取行动，被污染的废料就开始冒泡、渗出黏液，几只灵魂瘟疫躯壳随之苏醒"
"了！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4330
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SMOLDERINGREMAINS\"]/text"
msgstr "你急切地回应这道求救信号，映入眼帘的景象却令人不适……发出信号的飞船已经彻底损"
"毁，无法修复。它如今不过是一堆松散的废料，漂浮在云层之中。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4333
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SMOLDERINGREMAINS\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "该死……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4335
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SMOLDERINGREMAINS\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你在残骸中找到了求救信标，并彻底终止了它的信号。很遗憾你来晚了，但你希望在此"
"陨落的灵魂至少能安息。然而，你内心的另一部分却察觉到了一个机会……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4337
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SMOLDERINGREMAINS\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "确实是个机会！搜刮那片残骸！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4341
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SMOLDERINGREMAINS\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我们保持尊重，不要再惊扰这些遗骸了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4343
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SMOLDERINGREMAINS\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "有人在此丧生，你不会舍弃这些仅存的、证明他们存在过的痕迹。你心情沉重地转身离"
"开残骸，在超光速引擎充能时，找了个安静的地方独自沉思。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4345
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SMOLDERINGREMAINS\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4349
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SMOLDERINGREMAINS\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4360
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKAMBUSH_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "那艘船四分五裂，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4363
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKAMBUSH_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4368
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKAMBUSH_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr "敌方船员尽数死亡，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4371
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKAMBUSH_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4378
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKAMBUSH_FIGHT_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"这难道是躯壳设下的某种埋伏吗？想到这种可能性，你不寒而栗……但事已至此，除了继"
"续前进，你别无选择。至少，银河系里又少了一艘满载无脑行尸的飞船来骚扰各方。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4383
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKAMBUSH\"]/text"
msgstr "在星云的一处空旷地带，你没花多久就发现了那艘发出求救信号的飞船……可不幸的是，"
"你也很快意识到，驾驶它的正是躯壳！它们正朝这边过来！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4388
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DISTRESS_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKAMBUSH\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4402
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKSWAITING\"]/text"
msgstr "你本指望这片区域的星云稀薄地带会更安全一些，可这艘在附近来回颠簸的飞船，似乎"
"一心要粉碎你的希望……躯壳，来袭！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4405
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKSWAITING\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4412
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLBAIT_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "那艘船四分五裂，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4415
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLBAIT_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4420
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLBAIT_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr "敌方船员尽数死亡，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4423
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLBAIT_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4430
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLBAIT_FIGHT_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr "你开始意识到，无论是否身处这片星云内部，你都无法相信这片区域里的任何事物。这"
"里到处都是躯壳，你不禁好奇它们究竟已经扩散到了多远的地方……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4434
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLBAIT\"]/text"
msgstr "这里停着一艘甲壳族飞船，但它们并未理会你的到来。它们出现在这里很奇怪，不过你"
"觉得只要不在星云内部，待在任何地方都要好一些。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4437
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLBAIT\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "或许我们该引起它们的注意？向甲壳族发送通讯信号。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4439
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLBAIT\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你发出通讯请求，他们的飞船微微一动，随后像喝醉了一般来回摇晃……这些根本不是甲"
"壳族！他们松散的动作忽然变得紧绷，锁定了你的位置，你这才意识到，自己惊扰了一"
"个躯壳巢穴！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4442
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLBAIT\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4448
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLBAIT\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "哦，它们可以无视我，但我不会放过它们。攻击甲壳族！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4450
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLBAIT\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你靠近甲壳族，武器开始充能，他们的飞船微微一动，随后像喝醉了一般来回摇晃……这"
"些根本不是甲壳族！他们松散的动作忽然变得紧绷，锁定了你的位置，你这才意识到，"
"自己惊扰了一个躯壳巢穴！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4453
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLBAIT\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4459
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLBAIT\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "他们可以自顾自地待着。无视甲壳族。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4461
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLBAIT\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr "坦白说，你对它们为什么在这里并不感兴趣。你真正在意的是离开这里，而原地等待超"
"光速引擎充能，正是为了达成这个目标。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4463
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLBAIT\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4467
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_SHELLBAIT\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4475
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESPITE\"]/text"
msgstr "在如此动荡不安的星域里，安宁本就极为罕见，而你却成功找到了一处远离所有混乱的"
"寂静空地。你得趁这份平静还在时好好享受……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4477
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESPITE\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4481
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_RESPITE\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4495
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_EPSILONREMAINS_BOXINSIDES_HUSKATTACK\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"当最后一条锁链松开时，箱子开始震动……它的侧面猛然炸开，一股极度腐臭的气味弥漫"
"在空气中。你后退一步，一团黑色的黏稠物从裂口缓缓渗出，躯壳在你面前开始聚合！"
"哪怕就一次，你也希望能走运找到点战利品……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4500
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_EPSILONREMAINS_BOXINSIDES_FRIENDLYHUSK\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"最后一条锁链松开，你打开了箱子……一股极度腐臭的气味瞬间充斥空气中。你后退一步"
"，让眼睛适应箱子里的黑暗，随即发现自己正与一具躯壳面对面！你立刻摆出防御姿态"
"，可在意识到它还没有任何动作时，又迟疑了。若不是见过躯壳会融化成一滩滩失活物"
"质瘫在地上，你定会以为它已经死了……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4502
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_EPSILONREMAINS_BOXINSIDES_FRIENDLYHUSK\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "没时间犹豫了。开枪打那该死的东西！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4504
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_EPSILONREMAINS_BOXINSIDES_FRIENDLYHUSK\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "你摇了摇头，打破迟疑，朝躯壳开火。它在你开枪的瞬间活了过来，你立刻拔腿就跑！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4509
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_EPSILONREMAINS_BOXINSIDES_FRIENDLYHUSK\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "朝躯壳挥挥手。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4511
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_EPSILONREMAINS_BOXINSIDES_FRIENDLYHUSK\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你朝它挥了挥手，令你恶心的是，它居然也朝你挥了挥手。你再往后退一步，它就朝你"
"走近一步，你意识到它在隐约模仿你的动作……有点用，就是……呃……让人很不舒服。欢迎"
"加入队伍，躯壳……？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4512
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_EPSILONREMAINS_BOXINSIDES_FRIENDLYHUSK\"]/choice[2]/event/crewMember"
msgstr "镜中人"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4518
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_EPSILONREMAINS_BOXINSIDES_WEAPON\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"最后一条锁链松开，你打开了箱子……一股极度腐臭的气味弥漫在空气中。你后退一步，"
"让眼睛适应里面的黑暗，然后你看到了……一件武器。但这并非普通武器，而是一件完全"
"被灵魂瘟疫物质病毒侵染的武器！就算得小心安装，这也是个不错的发现。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4523
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_EPSILONREMAINS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"太空外漂浮着一个金属箱，每一端都被锁链紧紧锁住，除此之外没有任何特征。你试图"
"分辨里面装着什么，却徒劳无功，只能暗自疑惑自己面对的究竟是什么东西……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4525
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_EPSILONREMAINS\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "把这个奇怪的箱子带上舰。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4527
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_EPSILONREMAINS\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"把箱子弄进来并不算费力，可要挪动它却困难得多。等你把它放到满意的位置后，便能"
"更清楚地观察……它并非你所想的那样毫无特征，侧面依稀能辨认出一些褪色的刻字：\n"
"\n"
"“怪才体科学区 伊普西隆分部 财产”\n"
"\n"
"还好，你周围没有看到任何甲壳族，不会有人来找你劫掠的麻烦。现在只剩下打开箱子"
"这一步了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4533
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_EPSILONREMAINS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "砸断箱子上的锁链，打开它。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4537
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_EPSILONREMAINS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "转念一想……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4539
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_EPSILONREMAINS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "你一点也不信任这个箱子里的东西；谁知道怪才体的人在这里到底搞了什么勾当？你把"
"它扔回外面，看着它缓缓飘向远方……或许某天会有其他人发现它。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4541
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_EPSILONREMAINS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4545
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_EPSILONREMAINS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4553
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_EPSILONREMAINS\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "别碰这个箱子。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4555
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_EPSILONREMAINS\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"就算这里飘着的是用彩虹和糖果做的随机箱子，你也不会信任，更别说这是金属和锁链"
"打造的了……它有种说不出的感觉让你不安。你不去碰它，看着箱子缓缓飘向远方……或许"
"某天会有其他人发现它。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4557
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_EPSILONREMAINS\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4561
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_EPSILONREMAINS\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4570
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_AUTOMALFUNCTION_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "那艘船四分五裂，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4573
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_AUTOMALFUNCTION_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4580
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_AUTOMALFUNCTION_FIGHT_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你不敢相信自己竟然就这样被叛军打了个措手不及……这是一个教训：永远不要相信空荡"
"荡的信标，无论它们看起来多么平静！尤其是在这样一片荒凉阴郁的星域里……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4584
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_AUTOMALFUNCTION_SURPRISEATTACK\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"外面闪过一道强光，一艘叛军自动战舰咆哮着冲入信标区域——这里根本没有安宁可言！"
"它的武器开始充能，同时发出一段断断续续的自动讯息：“不——不要抵——抵抗。你的死——"
"死——死亡将会迅——迅速。”这东西的通讯系统到底多久没检修了，才会乱成这样？不过这"
"都不重要了……准备战斗！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4587
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_AUTOMALFUNCTION_SURPRISEATTACK\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4593
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_AUTOMALFUNCTION\"]/text"
msgstr "些许安宁与平静……虽不必习惯，却仍会好好珍惜。至少，这总比再遇上一群躯壳要好得"
"多。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4595
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_AUTOMALFUNCTION\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4599
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_AUTOMALFUNCTION\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4620
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"NEBULA_HOSTILE_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS_TEXT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr "当一艘飞船的阴影在外面的星云中隐隐出现时，你的心里一沉。你引起了它的注意，而"
"当它摇摇晃晃地逼近时，你最担心的事情还是发生了！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4621
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"NEBULA_HOSTILE_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS_TEXT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"灵魂瘟疫躯壳让你感到心神不宁。你说不清是因为它们本就是死亡的副产物，还是它们"
"发起攻击时从胸口迸发而出的无数触须，又或是它们那色彩斑驳的面容，嘲弄着孕育它"
"们的生命本身……但在它们再次对你的飞船发动攻击时，你有足够的时间去想明白这一切"
"！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4622
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"NEBULA_HOSTILE_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS_TEXT\"]/text[3]"
msgstr "有那么一瞬间，当你看到外面有一艘飞船时，心中闪过一丝希望……可当你注意到它们的"
"移动方式时，希望瞬间破灭。那又是一艘躯壳飞船，正朝这边驶来！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4623
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"NEBULA_HOSTILE_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS_TEXT\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"你感觉这片星域仿佛扼杀掉了一切生命迹象，而那些该死的躯壳就是它的刽子手。你不"
"确定将一片星域如此拟人化，是否意味着你有些精神失常，但事实是，下一个被送上断"
"头台的，很可能就是你。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4624
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"NEBULA_HOSTILE_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS_TEXT\"]/text[5]"
msgstr ""
"这些躯壳到底有没有尽头？它们为何要肆虐这片星域？当又一艘被它们占据的飞船颤抖"
"着、令人不安地逼近时，你默默发誓，一定要查清这些问题的真相……并终结它们的扩散"
"。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4625
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"NEBULA_HOSTILE_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS_TEXT\"]/text[6]"
msgstr ""
"你驶入信标时，一艘飞船从你身旁呼啸而过，但在它深入星云之前，你没能看清它的模"
"样。紧接着第二艘飞船驶来，航行姿态却摇晃得多……你立刻意识到，那是躯壳，而你似"
"乎已经吸引了它们的注意！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4629
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"NEBULA_HOSTILE_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS_STORM_TEXT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr "外面风暴中，一艘飞船的阴影隐隐浮现，你的心瞬间沉了下去。你引起了它的注意，当"
"它摇摇晃晃逼近时，你最恐惧的事情得到了证实！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4630
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"NEBULA_HOSTILE_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS_STORM_TEXT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr "有那么一瞬间，当你在风暴中看到一艘飞船时，心中闪过一丝希望……可当你注意到它的"
"移动方式时，希望瞬间破灭。那又是一艘躯壳飞船，正朝这边驶来！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4631
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"NEBULA_HOSTILE_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS_STORM_TEXT\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"你驶入信标时，一艘飞船从你身旁呼啸而过，但在它深入风暴之前，你没能看清它的模"
"样。紧接着第二艘飞船驶来，航行姿态却摇晃得多……你立刻意识到，那是躯壳，而你似"
"乎已经吸引了它们的注意！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4635
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"NEBULA_HOSTILE_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS_LIGHTNEBULA_TEXT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr "外面星云的空旷地带中，一艘飞船的阴影缓缓浮现，你的心瞬间沉了下去。你引起了它"
"的注意，当它摇摇晃晃逼近时，你最恐惧的事情得到了证实！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4636
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"NEBULA_HOSTILE_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS_LIGHTNEBULA_TEXT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"有那么一瞬间，当你在稀薄的星云中发现一艘飞船时，心中闪过一丝希望……可当你注意"
"到它的移动方式时，希望瞬间破灭。那又是一艘躯壳飞船，正朝这边驶来！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4637
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"NEBULA_HOSTILE_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS_LIGHTNEBULA_TEXT\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"你驶入信标时，一艘飞船从你身旁呼啸而过，你还没看清它的样子，它就从空旷地带退"
"回，重新隐入星云之中。紧接着第二艘飞船驶来，航行姿态却摇晃得多……你立刻意识到"
"，那是躯壳，而你似乎已经吸引了它们的注意！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4646
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_DESTROYED_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS\"]/text[1]"
msgstr "考虑到船上的存在，你在拆解这艘被躯壳侵染的飞船残骸时格外小心。要是不小心捡到"
"了受污染的废料，让一切循环重新开始，那可就糟了……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4647
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_DESTROYED_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS\"]/text[2]"
msgstr "躯壳飞船解体时，几块被灵魂瘟疫感染的物质向四面八方飞散，但你成功避开了它们的"
"轨迹，并在残骸中找到了可用的资源。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4648
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_DESTROYED_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS\"]/text[3]"
msgstr "总算摆脱了……又少了一批在星系里肆虐的躯壳。希望你为它们报了仇之后，这艘飞船原"
"先的主人能够安息。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4649
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_DESTROYED_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS\"]/text[4]"
msgstr "这事到此为止了。你不禁打了个寒颤，想到自己的飞船和船员也极有可能在物质病毒的"
"手中落得同样下场，但只要能持续战胜这些躯壳，就没什么好担心的。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4650
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_DESTROYED_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS\"]/text[5]"
msgstr ""
"摧毁被躯壳占据的飞船真是悲喜交加，但收获战利品的感觉显然就单纯多了。把这些丧"
"尸轰回地狱，再收集大量废料与资源……如果不是这片区域让人如此不适，你几乎要习惯"
"这种生活了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4651
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_DESTROYED_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS\"]/text[6]"
msgstr ""
"待在被灵魂瘟疫感染的残骸附近，只比面对那些还能正常运作的感染飞船稍微安全一点"
"，但你对自己的能力足够自信，能够分辨出正常物质和……那些令人作呕的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4660
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_DEAD_CREW_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS\"]/text[1]"
msgstr "穿行在被躯壳占据的飞船走廊中，空气中弥漫的不安感清晰可触。最好速战速决，别让"
"任何人踩进那些泛着虹彩的感染物质水洼里……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4661
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_DEAD_CREW_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS\"]/text[2]"
msgstr "虽然躯壳已经被解决，但你清楚，孕育出它们的物质病毒绝不可小觑。你一边小心地从"
"飞船残骸中收集能拿到的战利品，一边保持着警惕。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4662
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_DEAD_CREW_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS\"]/text[3]"
msgstr "当你漫步在刚清空的飞船内部时，不禁为它原先的乘客感到惋惜……我说的是那些，呃，"
"没有浑身油腻、也没有长着触须的家伙。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4663
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_DEAD_CREW_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS\"]/text[4]"
msgstr "躯壳或许十分强悍，但今天你在此证明了自己更胜一筹。如今它们不过是地板上的一滩"
"滩污迹，你可以自由地搜刮这艘被它们劫持的飞船内部了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4664
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_DEAD_CREW_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS\"]/text[5]"
msgstr "一场猛攻……但并非你无法战胜的攻势。在勇敢面对过这些不死的恐怖存在后，战利品如"
"今任你收取。只是记得千万别碰那些泛着彩色的东西，明白吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4665
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_DEAD_CREW_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS\"]/text[6]"
msgstr ""
"清理这些躯壳留下的烂摊子并不愉快，但至少它们死后留下的失活物质池，在死亡效应"
"消散后大多已无危险。不过，它们飞船上那些仍然处于激活状态的物质就没那么安全了"
"，需要格外仔细才能分辨出哪些是有价值的资源，哪些是致命的威胁。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4673
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_HOSTILE_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4684
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_HOSTILE_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4694
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_HOSTILE_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKS_STORM\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4700
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"NEBULA_HOSTILE_DDSOULPLAGUE_AUTO_TEXT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr "就算在这片区域，你也无法摆脱反叛军的影响……不过相比躯壳，你宁愿去炸毁那些自动"
"飞船。它们没那么脏乱，而且更……干脆。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4701
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"NEBULA_HOSTILE_DDSOULPLAGUE_AUTO_TEXT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"当他们的一艘自动飞船靠近时，一个念头闪过你的脑海：叛军可能会为了他们的邪恶目"
"的，将灵魂瘟疫物质病毒武器化。你只能希望整个银河都尚未充分利用腐化者系统……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4709
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_HOSTILE_DDSOULPLAGUE_AUTO\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4715
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"NEBULA_HOSTILE_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUG_TEXT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"星云里有一艘蛞蝓族飞船，从它流畅的航行姿态来看，并没有被躯壳侵占！可惜好消息"
"到此为止，因为它们已经将武器对准了你，并要求你交出所有贵重物品……有些事情永远"
"都不会变。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4716
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"NEBULA_HOSTILE_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUG_TEXT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"虽然你没有发现任何飞船，但在驶入信标时却收到了通讯请求。你试探性地接通，屏幕"
"另一端只映出一只蛞蝓族模糊的身影，它开口说道：“我才不管通灵会派多少联邦佬～～"
"过来，我就是绝不交税～～！”你还没来得及开口，对方就挂断了通讯。紧接着，它的飞"
"船从外面的云雾中现身，武器正在充能。通灵会究竟为何要派遣联邦舰船来收税，而一"
"只蛞蝓族宁愿躲在被躯壳肆虐的星域也不肯交税，这事儿为什么一点都不让你觉得意外"
"？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4724
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_HOSTILE_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUG\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4730
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"NEBULA_HOSTILE_DDSOULPLAGUE_GHOST_TEXT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"本来就很难分辨真正的残骸和被魂灵族占据的飞船，更别说附近还有躯壳在劫持属于它"
"们自己的舰船了。唯一能说明问题的迹象是，这艘破损的飞船正在稳步逼近，而且武器"
"正在充能！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4731
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//textList[@name=\"NEBULA_HOSTILE_DDSOULPLAGUE_GHOST_TEXT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"平常在这片地狱般的星域里，能找到一艘没有被躯壳侵染的飞船，你本该欣喜若狂，可"
"这里的魂灵族似乎对你的存在毫无善意。你不确定它们是把你们当成了躯壳，还是单纯"
"不喜欢你们，但无论如何，它们显然都决意要发动攻击！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4739
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_HOSTILE_DDSOULPLAGUE_GHOST\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4746
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "当炽天使崩解、炸裂的那一刻，一道尖锐却又圣洁的嘶吼在你脑海中回响……你活下来了"
"！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4749
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4754
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr "当炽天使倒下，他们的飞船崩解爆炸时，一道尖锐却又神圣的呼喊在你脑海中回响……你"
"活下来了！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4759
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4766
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED_NOMOREQUESTIONS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"老人站起身，拍了拍盔甲上的灰尘：“如果事情就到此为止，那我想我们最好还是上路吧"
"。虽然我们之间有分歧，但你今天确实帮了我，尽管这困境一开始就是你的错……我觉得"
"最好还是跟你同行一段时间，至少，直到风暴之令另有指示为止。”他正要转身离开，你"
"却突然想起，心里还有一个问题想问……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4768
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED_NOMOREQUESTIONS\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "等等，你叫什么名字？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4770
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED_NOMOREQUESTIONS\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他转向你，脸上带着一丝轻笑：“在我披上这身盔甲时，风暴之令便收走了我真正的名字"
"，不过……你可以像我的下属一样，叫我大臣。或是风暴之手，哪个都行。”你能感觉到，"
"他很喜欢这些称号……不管怎样，你们是时候出发了。谁也说不准，在星云更深处，还有"
"怎样疯狂的事物在等待着你们。但在准备启程时，你的心中却多了一份暖意，一份慰藉—"
"—你不必再独自面对这些恐怖了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4773
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED_NOMOREQUESTIONS\"]/choice/event/crewMember"
msgstr "大臣"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4775
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED_NOMOREQUESTIONS\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "那我们出发吧！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4777
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED_NOMOREQUESTIONS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "可就在你准备启程时……星云云雾中的某个东西吸引了你的注意。你很快便认出那是什么—"
"—一道缝合多元宇宙的裂隙。这一定就是炽天使们前来守护的东西……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4784
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED_NOMOREQUESTIONS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theshade\"]/text"
msgstr "（暗影）在你身后，那个身披斗篷的身影动了……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4786
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED_NOMOREQUESTIONS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theshade\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你第一次看见暗影在没有敌人的情况下行动。你注意到它的目光死死盯着外面的时空异"
"常点……你突然反应过来。你以前见过这种时空缝隙——就在你第一次遇见暗影的时候，在"
"黑暗之神的领域里……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4788
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED_NOMOREQUESTIONS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theshade\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4790
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED_NOMOREQUESTIONS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theshade\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你正思索着这一切，几乎没注意到暗影的斗篷里有什么东西亮了起来……而外面的空间裂"
"隙也随之开始共振。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4798
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED_NOMOREQUESTIONS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theshade\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "等等，你在干什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4800
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED_NOMOREQUESTIONS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theshade\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你没有得到任何口头回答——相反，你收到了一个非常、非常直接的回应……一道冲击波从"
"裂隙中轰然爆发，你的飞船正以难以置信的速度被吸进去！根本逃不掉——你必须立刻抓"
"住身边的东西，快！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4803
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED_NOMOREQUESTIONS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theshade\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "伸手抓住点什么！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4816
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED_NOMOREQUESTIONS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "远离那个诡异的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4818
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED_NOMOREQUESTIONS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "你自己完全没有相关专业知识，也根本没打算去触碰这东西——谁知道你会掉进什么恐怖"
"的现实里！你只想离这条宇宙裂隙远远的，便再次准备出发。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4828
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"循着痕迹，你果然找到了那位老人……但却没看到他的飞船。不清楚究竟出了什么事、又"
"是如何发生的，他的躯体就这样飘浮在太空中……一动不动。他的生命体征显示为零。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4830
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "回收老人的遗体。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4832
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你心情沉重地下令把他的遗体带回舰内。凑近一看，他的脸部已被严重烧伤，若不是身"
"上那套独特的盔甲，你根本认不出是他。你正想着有没有办法能让他复苏，手指却不经"
"意擦过盔甲胸口嵌着的一颗白色球体，电流骤然在球体周围迸发，将你猛地弹开！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4834
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "满怀敬畏地注视着。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4836
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你后退几步，保持距离，看着电流越来越强，最终在老人的身体周围形成了一层类似茧"
"状的包裹。随着一声震耳欲聋的轰鸣，电光消散，老人猛地吸了一口气，直挺起身：“啊"
"！啊，以上方的风暴之名，感谢一切神圣存在，你收到了我的讯息。我之前还担心……”他"
"仔细看向你，脸上的释然瞬间化为难看的皱眉，“……会先被某个混混发现。看来你确实活"
"下来了……而且，居然比我的手下先找到我。不错。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4838
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你就是这么报答我的吗？我刚刚可是救了你一命！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4840
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"老人用护腕擦了擦脸，你才发现他脸上的烧伤已经奇迹般地痊愈了。“你根本什么都没救"
"到！顶多也就救了你自己而已。我早就说过，我几乎肯定能活下来，我是说真的。不管"
"是你、我的手下，还是这片可怕星域里那些令人憎恶的躯壳找到我都一样，只要我进入"
"适合生存的环境，就一定会复活。这就是风暴的意志。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4842
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "风暴？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4844
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他筋疲力尽又满心烦躁地重新跪了下来：“算是我的庇护者吧，如果你听得懂的话。我们"
"并不算意见相合，但为了让我的工作能继续下去，我只能交换条件——完成这些该死的任"
"务！偏偏还撞上了炽天使！这身盔甲虽然让我近乎不死，但被焚烧的感觉一点也不好受"
"！看这样子，那些混蛋也把我的飞船毁掉了……”男人又一次用手按住太阳穴，你能感觉到"
"他经常这么做……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4846
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你的庇护者？你的工作？任务？炽天使？我有很多问题……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4848
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他低低呻吟了一声，攥紧了空着的那只手，随后用一种认命般的语气松了口：“我想我暂"
"时是被困在这儿了。看来这次偶遇，比我想象的更像是命中注定……我猜，不管我愿不愿"
"意，风暴都是要我留在这里。好吧，我会回答你的问题，好斗的家伙。尽管问吧……”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4850
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "你刚才说风暴是你的庇护者。这到底意味着什么？他们究竟是谁？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4852
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“它算不上是谁，而是什么。据我所知，风暴是一个无比宏伟的造物，位于维系我们现实"
"的裂隙之外的领域，一个类似……口袋次元的地方。多年前，我倾尽一切抵达这片所谓的"
"应许之地，与那个存在会面……据说它能赐予奇迹，实现人最宏大的愿望。可我只觉得，"
"它除了玩弄我之外，什么都没做！”男人顿了顿，指了指自己的盔甲，“我花了仿佛永恒"
"的时间才让它注意到我，而它终于回应我时，却将我烙印进了这套该死的盔甲！我被迫"
"穿上它已经数十年，从未摆脱过它的禁锢。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4854
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "它到底是什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4856
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他叹了口气，“我也说不清。风暴用它以自己的方式控制着我……派我去执行这些毫无意义"
"的送死任务。不过这也并非毫无好处；这套盔甲让我无法死去，而且风暴赐予的力量中"
"还有不少极为实用的能力。对某些人来说永生或许是种诅咒，但是……我在这世上有一项"
"使命，我绝不能失败。这套盔甲以它的方式保证了这一点。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4858
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "这些信息有点多……我们先缓一缓。我们之前交战的甲壳族也提到过这些裂隙，它们到底"
"是什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4860
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你提起你遭遇过的那些怪异甲壳族，男人的脸色更加难看了。“炽天使……没错，他们一心"
"要确保这些裂隙不被打破，也可以说，是要让那些想闯入他们领地的跨次元旅行者无法"
"得逞。”他带着审视的目光打量着你，“我……猜你应该对宇宙簇理论一无所知吧？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4862
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "我……呃，确实没听说过。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4864
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“我不怪你；在我还是反抗军工程师的时候，光是提出这个理论可能有点道理，就差点被"
"部队开除。”他注意到你闻言绷紧了身体，便翻了个白眼，“那也是很多年前的事了，变"
"元者。我现在对他们可没什么好感，自从……”男人顿了顿，摇了摇头，“……算了。宇宙簇"
"理论往轻了说也算不上科学，支撑它的证据充其量也很牵强，但它认为，我们多元宇宙"
"中的各个现实，是由相似的定义特征分割开来的；比方说，没人见过一个完全由巧克力"
"布丁构成的次元。这个理论认为，原因就在于，没有任何和我们相近的现实可能完全由"
"巧克力布丁构成，我们只会找到和自己这个‘簇’更相符的现实；比如说，某个次元里的"
"蛞蝓毫无理由地喜欢吃巧克力布丁。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4866
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "好吧……那张炽天使又在这其中扮演什么角色？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4868
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他摸了摸下巴，“如果一个完全由巧克力布丁构成的次元听起来很离谱，那你再想想一个"
"几乎全是火焰与硫磺的次元。炽天使就来自那里；一个对我们而言完全陌生的地狱，但"
"对他们来说却是家园。我……曾经去过那里，那时候炽天使对外来者还没这么有敌意。他"
"们的现实是离风暴所在的口袋次元最近的一个，因此也相当于通往那里的直接门户。问"
"题就出在……多元宇宙的裂隙上。无论你是否相信宇宙簇理论，我都已经亲手收集到足够"
"证据，证明有些现实无疑比我们所熟悉的那些更难进入。比如说，想要进入炽天使的现"
"实，就必须找到并精准利用时空缝隙。炽天使把这些缝隙称为‘裂隙破损’，我在短暂闯"
"入他们的现实后，也沿用了这个说法。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4870
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "该死，好吧……这信息量太大了。你刚才说炽天使以前没这么有敌意。到底发生了什么事"
"？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4872
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“我自己也不清楚详细缘由。从我后来和他们极少的接触来看，他们似乎开始憎恨风暴，"
"以及任何想要和它产生交集的人。也许是因为它所在位置的特殊性，又或者是因为人们"
"必须穿过他们的现实才能抵达那里？我很难说清，但事实就是，他们会拼命守护这些裂"
"隙破损，就像你今天亲眼所见的那样。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4874
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "说到这儿……那你就是为此而来的吗？为了破开裂隙，再次进入炽天使的现实？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4876
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他摇了摇头，“以风暴之名，我才没有。我再也不想见识那个地狱了。是风暴下令的，我"
"就得照做。就这么简单，就算我想质疑也做不到。我最多只能推测，它想让这条裂隙为"
"某人或某物敞开，然后利用我来确保这一点。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4878
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "如果裂隙已经敞开，那……我们能进去吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4880
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"老人笑了起来，“除非你活腻了！就算你真想找死，这裂隙也才刚刚被打通而已。想要精"
"准抵达你想去的次元，必须进行精密操作，否则你说不定会不小心淹死在巧克力布丁里"
"。”你用一种眼神看着他，他的脸色沉了下来，“不行，我不会为了满足你的好奇心去做"
"任何所谓的精密操作。你想死的话，可以去找别的懂行的人，但我敢说，但凡知情的人"
"，都不会疯到答应这种事。很久以前我那么做，也只是因为我觉得自己别无选择……”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4882
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "好吧……你一直都在暗示这件事。那究竟是什么，驱使你穿越地狱、去求见风暴的？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4884
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“我之前……稍微提过我和叛军有关。详细来说，我曾在万斯的首席工程师团队中任职；我"
"的任务是完善多元宇宙引擎，为叛军争取对抗敌对势力的优势。我们要破开其他人连想"
"都不敢想的现实壁垒，用最简单的方式确保叛军的胜利。正是在研究这个项目的过程中"
"，我偶然发现了宇宙簇理论，还有……一些更黑暗的发现。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4886
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "更黑暗的发现？比如什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4888
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他打了个寒颤，“证据显示，存在着远比我们的世界更恐怖的次元；这些证据表明，我们"
"试图逃离与0号宇宙相似的熟悉次元，是在犯下一个弥天大错。即便在当时，我也深感不"
"安，但叫停项目并非我能决定……直到今天，我仍不清楚那些命令究竟来自何方。某个身"
"居高位的蠢货，被荣耀的承诺冲昏了头脑，完全不去考虑后果。而那些后果，却要由我"
"来承担！那些后果……还要由我的女儿来承担。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4890
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "你的女儿……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4892
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“是的，我亲爱的伊芙琳……”有那么一瞬间，他的声音近乎哽咽，但你能感觉到，当他失"
"神望向远方时，这件事他已经悲痛了太久，久到再也挤不出为她而流的眼泪。过了片刻"
"，他继续说道：“那是实验室里再平常不过的一天，我们正在测试一台多元宇宙引擎原型"
"机。她执意要过来看看，而我……是个糟糕的父亲。我不忍心拒绝她，然后一切就……”他又"
"顿了顿，目光落在地面上。“实验出了故障，引擎开始撕裂整个空间。在她被卷入次元漩"
"涡之前，我最后看到的，就是她对我露出的笑容，仿佛只要我在，就没有什么能伤害到"
"她……”他的身躯愈发佝偻，随后才再次开口：“我彻底崩溃了。我们在造成更大损失前关"
"掉了引擎，但一切都已经太晚了。我感觉，我失去了一切。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4894
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "我明白了。我很抱歉……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4896
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"老人抬头看着你，“不必道歉。我只能怪我自己……而且我也确实一直在自责。虽然我之后"
"还在叛军待了一段时间，但那时候多半只是个幌子，用来推进我自己的目标。我的目标"
"是找到她……把伊芙琳带回来……”他再次失神地望向虚空，“我后来遇到了一个男人。他身"
"着金色丝绸长袍，华美得超乎我所有想象。我把自己的困境告诉了他；我甚至说不出原"
"因，但我就是觉得可以信任他。他只是点头，静静听我悲叹。到最后，这成了一种习惯"
"，我们经常这样见面，算是某种倾诉……直到有一天，他给了我一个解决办法。他向我说"
"起了风暴，说起它如何实现愿望。说起现实之间的裂隙，以及如何从那里抵达它的所在"
"。这一切听上去都疯疯癫癫，可我当时……太绝望了。我偷走了一台多元宇宙引擎，按照"
"那个男人的指示去做。那是我最后一次见到他，也是我最后一次与叛军有牵扯……从那次"
"旅程结束起，我就成了风暴之手。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4898
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "所以，你为风暴效力，可是……你的愿望实现了吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4900
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN_OLDMANLOCATED\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“我不知道。已经过去这么久了，风暴从未对我说过一句话。我唯一能做的，就是透过这"
"套铠甲，遵从它的意志……掌管它的教派，执行它的仪式，传播它的恩惠。我完全不知道"
"这一切究竟是为了什么。”他看着你，眼中满是悲伤，“我只能祈祷，在这段旅程的终点"
"，风暴能实现我的愿望，让我再见到她。”"

