#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4996
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你重重地松了一口气，等待着那位奇怪老人的回音。但比他本人更诡异的是……那通联络"
"始终没有到来。他该不会就这么不辞而别了吧？你还没拿到属于你的战利品呢！或许……"
"你能在这片星云中找到他的飞船？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4999
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddtempest_stormborn_spawn\"]/text"
msgstr "（风暴诞生物）看向你得到的那只巨型团块，答案就在其中。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5001
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddtempest_stormborn_spawn\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"尽管你说不清是什么驱使着自己，还是靠近了那怪异的东西，凑得非常近。你能听见它"
"每一根纤维都在蠕动，它的嘴在咬合，它的眼睛在眨动……而你凝视着它那许多不停眨动"
"的眼睛。你感觉到了……一种联结。不是与你，而是与附近某个地方。你无法解释，但你"
"仿佛仅凭这东西与老人之间的联系，就确切知晓了他的位置……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5003
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"ddtempest_stormborn_spawn\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "循着这股奇异的感觉走。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5009
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_SLUG\"]/text"
msgstr "（蛞蝓族船员）让你的蛞蝓尝试定位他。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5011
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_SLUG\"]/event/text"
msgstr "你的蛞蝓族望向外面广袤的太空，在远处捕捉到了一个微弱的信号……重点是，非常微弱"
"。是不是出什么问题了？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5013
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_SLUG\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "跟随你的蛞蝓族探测到的信号前进。"

