#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5049
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[6]/text"
msgstr "亲自去找他。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5051
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER_SERAPHIMPROPHET_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice[6]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你明知这是徒劳之举，却还是忍不住要试一试……可惜，在星云这般广袤的区域里手动搜"
"寻一艘飞船，根本就是白费力气。几分钟的搜索过后，你没有找到那位老人的任何踪迹"
"，直觉告诉你，再找多久也不会有任何改变。是时候空手离开了……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5065
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "那艘奇异水晶运输船的坐标指向了这个位置。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5067
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER\"]/text"
msgstr "你已经抵达了这处神秘坐标……可即便如此，就算这里真有什么东西，在星云之中你也完"
"全无法分辨。这片区域的太空和其他地方一样，死寂一片。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5070
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "这里一定有什么东西！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5072
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"仿佛是为了证明你的话没错，就在你焦躁不已的时候，一通来自未知位置的通讯接入了"
"。你满心期待着拿到应得的战利品，立刻接通通讯，映入眼帘的是一位身着黑色铠甲的"
"老者背影，他正在摆弄着某个看不见的东西。“维多林，你又迟到了！你还指望我亲自处"
"理这些事吗？时机就快到了，多亏了你和你教派的拖延，我们几乎没时间准备仪式了。"
"告诉我，你至少把束缚试剂带来了吧？”你一时不知该如何回应，片刻后，老者又重复了"
"一遍：“怎么？你带来了，对不对？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5074
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我……呃……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5076
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你结结巴巴地说不出话，那人转过身来。“你是故意——”他看到你时，话说到一半突然停"
"住，眨了几下眼，然后用手指按着太阳穴，脸上露出不耐烦的神情。“你不是维多林。告"
"诉我，你是怎么找到我这个荒无人烟的地方的？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5078
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我……我……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5080
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"就在你支支吾吾时，他打断了你：“算了，这不重要。我们快没时间了……看来只能用麻烦"
"的办法了。”男人微微偏过头，像是想越过你的肩膀看向别处，随后摇了摇头，叹了口气"
"：“你的飞船只能将就用了。虽然没什么特别的，但看起来还算能用。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5082
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "什么？你在说什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5084
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“你居然会说话！算我开眼了。入侵者，给我听仔细。我不管你是用什么手段对付维多林"
"的教派才摸到这里，为了即将到来的事，我只能先不计较。”他一只手仍按着太阳穴，另"
"一只手朝舷窗示意。“我们俩都能活下来的路只有一条——或者说，你能活下来的路只有一"
"条。我是肯定死不了的，但这无关紧要。你必须在我进行束缚仪式时顶住他们的主力攻"
"势……都怪你捣乱，我没有束缚试剂了，可只要你不死，就还能成。你做得到吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5086
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "等等。他们的人？你话说得还是太含糊了……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5088
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"男人用铠甲包裹的拳头狠狠砸在控制台：炽天使，该死的！他们就快——他话音未落，外"
"面一道强光瞬间吞没了你们，那耀眼的光芒甚至穿透了周围的星云，你只觉得一阵眩晕…"
"…"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5091
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "稳住心神。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5093
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"当你缓缓苏醒，刺眼的光芒渐渐褪去，你发现取而代之的是一艘甲壳族飞船，周身缠绕"
"着炽烈夺目的火焰。老者看到这艘飞船时，烦躁的神情瞬间消失，他压低声音低语：他"
"们来了。记住：千万别死。战斗一旦打响，我会尽我所能提供少量支援。别想逃跑，我"
"已经让你跑不掉了。就当是维多林最后的致意吧。你检查后确认，你的超光速引擎不知"
"为何已被能量过载，暂时瘫痪……看来你只能照老人说的去做。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5096
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "深吸一口气，面对这艘燃烧的飞船。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5098
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"男人结束了通讯，甲壳族主动向你发起了通讯。你这才意识到，他们并非普通的甲壳族—"
"—巨大而炽烈的光翼从他们背后展开，环绕在身侧，几乎形成了第二层甲壳。当你沉浸在"
"这震撼的景象中时，其中一个开口了：“原来，是联邦的变元者，想要利用位面缝隙中的"
"这处破绽……惩罚这份狂妄、封锁此处破绽，是我们的职责。在光芒中燃烧、忏悔吧，让"
"你体内的污秽得以净化，让我们重归安宁！”你能想象，这显然是谈判彻底破裂的意思。"
"可你到底卷入了什么事？缝隙？污秽？燃烧？尤其是最后那个词，让你心头一紧……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5102
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5104
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"又是一道强光闪过，一道闪电击中了你的飞船，你再次陷入失明。你眨了几下眼睛恢复"
"视线，眼前出现的竟是你之前击倒过的那种怪异触须怪物！只不过它看起来并没有那么"
"凶……这就是那老头所谓的支援吗？！但也只能这样了，燃烧的甲壳族飞船正在逼近，做"
"好战斗准备！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5106
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/crewMember"
msgstr "米斯特斯克"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5108
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5128
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "终焉装甲仿佛在注视着你。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5130
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_QUEST_DDSOULPLAGUE_THEMINISTER\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr "就算这里真的藏着什么，你也隐隐感到，终焉装甲并不希望你找到它……看来你只能空手"
"离开，只留下满心失落。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5136
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ENCOUNTER_DDSOULPLAGUE_ELITE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"怪才体通常负责保卫甲壳族的星域，但不知为何，他们的一艘舰船出现在了这片星云里"
"。你正打算上前询问缘由，他们却已转向你，武器开始充能！他们显然把你当成了威胁"
"！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5140
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ENCOUNTER_DDSOULPLAGUE_ELITE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5150
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "当你进入这片星域时，你就注意到了这个位置及其受损的数据。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5152
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/text"
msgstr "那座带有标记的奇异信标，似乎把你引到了星云里的一片空旷地带，可是……这里除此之"
"外，什么都没有吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5156
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "我什么也没看见。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5158
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你对着这座空无一物的信标自语，一个突兀的念头闯入脑海：\n"
"\n"
"只因你尚无看见它的双眼。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5162
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "能看见的双眼……这是什么意思？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5164
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"身后传来一阵爆炸，你被冲击波狠狠撞在飞船控制台之上。你转过身，只见一个全身覆"
"甲的身影，正从某种传送门中挣脱出来——与其说是走出，不如说是奋力杀出。他手中的"
"长矛不断撕裂那些黏腻油滑、试图将他拖回去的触须。你瞬间认出了这些触须……这是被"
"灵魂瘟疫感染的物质！你惊愕地看着那道身影斩断所有触须，身后的传送门随之关闭。"
"他稍作清理，失活的灵魂瘟疫残骸溅落在地板上，随后转向你，指着自己，终于开口："
"\n"
"\n"
"“意思就是……你需要一点帮忙！”\n"
"\n"
"你感觉这句话在他自己心里应该挺酷的，但你还是不太明白之前那句暗语是什么意思。"
"不过至少你能听出他的声音：虽然被头盔闷住，但明显是女性声线，带着戏剧感，又透"
"着疲惫——尤其是疲惫。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5171
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "好吧，呃……女士？你是谁？还有，你经常通过传送门闯入别人的飞船吗……？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5173
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "“闯入——你会在这里，就是因为收到了我的讯息，对吗？你收到了，没错吧？”她并不反"
"对你叫她女士，这事就算这么定了。至于她所说的讯息……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5175
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你是说那串奇怪的押韵文字吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5177
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"她双手护腕相抵，长矛仍握在手中，样子有些局促：“对！你回应了英雄的召唤！太好了"
"，我们没多少时间可以浪费了。那些星之子……呃，仔细想想，或许该叫织命者……不重要"
"！重点是，他们随时会过来把我抓回去。你，呃……”她仔细打量了你一番，气势弱了几分"
"，“……你不是我们的人。难怪你看不见。不过没关系，你还是回应了召唤！你有一颗英雄"
"的心，这就够了！只是这么一来，事情就有点尴尬了……你知道现在到底发生了什么吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5179
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "完全不知道。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5181
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"我明白了……好吧，你现在是我唯一的机会了，我可不想再等上一辈子！我尽量长话短说"
"。她整理了一下思绪，然后用覆甲的手按住心口：很久以前……不，这么说太蠢了。听着"
"。有个东西一心要把我困住，一个古老、邪恶又精于算计的存在。它会操控一群甲壳族"
"来达到目的，甚至不惜葬送整个多元宇宙。你既然已经靠近了他们的核心区域，肯定见"
"过它所作所为留下的痕迹，对吧？她指向飞船外，好奇地注视着你。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5183
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你是说灵魂瘟疫物质病毒吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5185
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"这位铠甲女杰点了点头：“你想怎么称呼它都无所谓；它的本质，就是熵的化身。它算不"
"上一种‘物质’病毒——尽管这个名字也算贴切——它更像是一种‘时空’病毒。据我所知，它"
"被扭曲改造，唯一目的就是让我永远受折磨。那些无意间创造出它的甲壳族，原本想要"
"的是完美的拟态体：一种可以模仿任何事物、任何人的特性，用来充当劳力的存在。他"
"们差一点就成功了，可最终还是在最后一步功亏一篑……正是这份绝望，迫使他们签下了"
"一笔他们根本无法理解后果的交易。他们的拟态体被黑暗力量扭曲，变成了你现在所说"
"的灵魂瘟疫物质病毒：一台用来腐化物质、并用其构建异次元监狱的机器。这所监狱扭"
"曲着空间与时间的法则，只为达成一个目的：永远把我囚禁在这里。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5187
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "嗯……你看起来可不太像被囚禁的样子。就这点来说，也不像在什么异次元里。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5189
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"她双手一摊：“喂！你少跟我冷嘲热讽！抵挡一波又一波没脑子的触手怪可不容易……大概"
"……一、二……四……呃，我都记不清了，反正好几百年了吧？天啊，说真的……你是这事开始"
"以来，我第一个说话的人。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5191
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "等等，好几百年？！是真的吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5193
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“对，真的有几百年！不过……也不全是。就像我刚才说的，这座异次元监狱并不遵循多元"
"宇宙其他地方的法则——它是一个真正意义上的额外维度。它叠加在时间、空间等一切事"
"物之上，却又对它们视而不见……至少大部分时候是这样。它并不完美，一部分力量还是"
"会渗漏出去，这就是你们所说的物质病毒出现的原因。但这种渗漏具有迷惑性，它吞噬"
"的绝大部分东西，最终都会涌向我这边……和我被迫面对的汪洋相比，你见到的只不过是"
"几缕浪花而已。”她一只手放在腰边，另一只手高高举起，仿佛不用这个动作就不足以说"
"明她的意思。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5195
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "好吧，那你呢……就这么从这片汪洋里逃出来了？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5197
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"她收回双手，摇了摇头，哦，我多希望我能做到。我现在只是在借时间……是我在这些无"
"穷无尽的战斗里，一点点攒下来的时间。我要用这段时间，彻底终结这场噩梦！她毫无"
"征兆地提高了音量，可在注意到吓到你之后，又冷静了下来。好吧，说实话，那些折磨"
"我的家伙随时都会回来。这就是你要做的——等他们把我抓回去时，我希望你跟上来。正"
"常情况下，我绝不会把任何人牵扯进来，但我怕已经没有别的办法能结束这场疯狂了。"
"相信我，我试过了，可我等得越久……它渗漏出来的力量就有越多时间吞噬下方的现实世"
"界。你确实见识过这片星域的现状……如果不采取行动，这物质病毒有朝一日会不会也侵"
"占其他星域？它的扩张会有尽头吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5199
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "那我该做什么？你看起来……呃，本事很大的样子。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5201
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的话似乎稍稍满足了她的自尊心：“我就算再厉害，终究也只有一个人。那片所谓的海"
"洋扩张速度，远远超过我能镇压的速度，而且它总能精准阻止我靠近它的核心。可如果"
"你能亲自抵达那里，为我争取足够的时间突围……我就能全力一击，彻底终结它的腐化！”"
"这位铠甲女杰摆出一副胜利的姿态，你忍不住有点尴尬。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5203
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你确定这个核心真的存在吗？而且它就是维持物质病毒运转的唯一东西？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5205
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"她点了点头，“你很快就会明白我的意思，就算你现在还不明白。它有一种能钻进你脑子"
"里的手段。不管是好是坏，到现在为止，它的整个蜂巢心智所知道的事情，我觉得没有"
"我不知道的。”你对这听起来疯狂的说法微微眯起眼，但她似乎没有注意到，只是把长矛"
"指向空中，“现在告诉我——你会是我寻找的那位同伴英雄吗？就此离开并不算丢人；虽然"
"再得到一次这样的机会会很麻烦，但我痛恨把这么可怕的任务强加给任何人，而且我无"
"法保证你和你这里的同伴能活着出去。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5207
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "这听起来很荒唐，但是……管他呢，我加入。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5209
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"她将长矛的尾端重重砸在地面，发出一声响亮的金属撞击声，再次将手按在胸口：“这才"
"是英雄该有的气魄！不为别的，只为正义而战……英雄就是这样诞生的。既然你要与我一"
"同深入巨兽的腹地，那你就需要这个！”她摊开手掌，微微用力……你一时不知道会发生什"
"么，紧接着，一团璀璨而炽热的火焰从她指尖的空气中猛然迸发！她收回手，金色的火"
"焰悬停在原地：“这……是希望。监狱里的星之子，或是更可怕的织命者，一旦你进入他们"
"的领域，必定会试图与你交易。他们可能许诺力量、自由、安宁，任何东西；全都是谎"
"言，唯一目的就是引你走向死亡。而希望，就是用来对抗这一切的。它是我力量的一部"
"分，也是我被囚禁的根源……它会成为你在即将到来的黑暗中的火炬。唤醒它，你就能燃"
"尽疑虑的阴影，揭露真相……至于真相究竟是什么，取决于你自己。我只希望你谨慎使用"
"，因为它的力量有限。”她示意你接过火焰，你迟疑地用双手捧住……它却没有灼伤你。相"
"反，你感到一阵安心与温暖。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5212
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "好吧，我会小心使用的。那么，那些抓你的人大概什么时候会回来？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5214
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"嗯……这比我预想的要久一些，可是——她话音未落，虚空中又一道传送门在她身后开启！"
"这道门比她进来时的要大得多，一团灵魂瘟疫感染的聚合体从中喷涌而出，从四面八方"
"缠住了她。你立刻上前想要帮忙，可她在被拖拽的间隙艰难地朝你大喊：别管我！让它"
"抓走我——你必须跟进来！你……一定要找到核心！只有你能——她的话被彻底打断，灵魂瘟"
"疫的浪潮将她完全吞没，成功把她拖了进去，随后传送门关闭。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5216
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "等等！我该怎么跟过去啊？！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5218
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "尽管寂静得令人窒息，你却以另一种方式得到了答案——外界的空间开始扭曲、变形……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5220
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5222
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"……而且就在这时，一团无比巨大的物质出现了，与此同时，无数道彩虹色的虫洞也在零"
"星生成。看来就是这里了……你早已下定决心，随即飞向其中一道虫洞。做好准备，你即"
"将进入光速！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5225
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "抓紧了！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5240
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "抱歉，我就不去了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5242
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"她动作里的能量淡去了一丝，她再次点了点头：“那……就当我没说过吧。是我错把你当成"
"英雄了……不过没关系！总有一天，我会找到我需要的帮助。在那之前……”她说话时，另一"
"道传送门在她身后出现，她主动朝它走去：“……祝你在自己的战斗里好运。”传送门吞没"
"了她，随即关闭，只留下你在一片寂静中。你心里有一丝愧疚，但……你确实有你自己的"
"难关要过。你只能继续前行。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5260
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我懂，不用解释。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:5262
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_DDSOULPLAGUE_BEACONOFHOPE_QUEST\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
